.insider.com%2F69c9d8748e5f53c45ea2d3ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223399%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E12%20tons%20of%20KitKats%20were%20stolen%20in%20transit%20between%20Italy%20and%20Poland.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Carter%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20major%20chocolate%20heist%20saw%20more%20than%20400%2C000%20bars%20of%20chocolate%20go%20missing%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENestl%C3%A9%20said%2012%20tons%20of%20KitKats%20were%20stolen%20between%20Italy%20and%20Poland.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20said%20supply%20would%20not%20be%20affected%20because%20of%20the%20robbery.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENestl%C3%A9%20said%20it%20was%20the%20target%20of%20a%20major%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-store-bought-chocolate-brands-chocolatier-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echocolate%20heist%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20confirm%20that%2012T%20of%20KitKat%20products%20were%20stolen%20while%20in%20transit%20between%20our%20factory%20in%20Central%20Italy%20and%20their%20destination%20in%20Poland%2C%26quot%3B%20KitKat%20said%20in%20a%20Sunday%20Instagram%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20it%20was%20working%20with%20local%20authorities%20and%20supply%20chain%20partners%20to%20investigate%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20good%20news%3A%20there%20are%20no%20concerns%20for%20consumer%20safety%2C%20and%20supply%20is%20not%20affected%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20media%20outlets%20reported%20that%2012%20tons%20amounts%20to%20more%20than%20400%2C000%20bars%20of%20the%20crunchy%20wafer%20chocolate%2C%20and%20that%20the%20robbery%20happened%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bars%20weren't%20regular%20KitKats%2C%20but%20rather%20special%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ff1-singapore-grand-prix-first-heat-hazard-race-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFormula%201%3C%2Fa%3E%20bars%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20F1%20cars%2C%20per%20reporting%20from%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%20KitKat%20announced%20in%20June%20last%20year%20that%20it%20was%20an%20official%20partner%20for%20the%20motorcar%20racing%20league.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-x-case-alleging-advertisers-boycott-platform-dismissed-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENestl%C3%A9%20took%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20opportunity%20to%20make%20some%20chocolate%20jokes%20in%20its%20statements%20to%20multiple%20media%20outlets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhilst%20we%20appreciate%20the%20criminals'%20exceptional%20taste%2C%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20cargo%20theft%20is%20an%20escalating%20issue%20for%20businesses%20of%20all%20sizes%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Nestl%C3%A9%20spokesperson%20told%20the%20LA%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20always%20encouraged%20people%20to%20have%20a%20break%20with%20KitKat%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Nestl%C3%A9%20spokesperson%20said%20to%20The%20Guardian.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20seems%20thieves%20have%20taken%20the%20message%20too%20literally%20and%20made%20a%20break%20with%20more%20than%2012%20tons%20of%20our%20chocolate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKitKat%20is%20an%20important%20product%20for%20Nestl%C3%A9.%20The%20Swiss%20food%20company%20said%20in%20its%20full-year%202025%20report%20that%20its%20confectionery%20business%20grew%208.2%25%20to%208.70%20billion%20Swiss%20Francs%2C%20or%20about%20%2410.89%20billion.%20This%20was%20led%20by%20KitKat%20sales%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENestl%C3%A9%20stock%20price%20is%20down%20more%20than%2010%25%20in%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnestle-kitkats-stolen-european-highway-heist-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774841474000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c9e7768373a547629c773e%3Fformat