in%20terms%20of%20%26quot%3Bharmony%26quot%3B%20instead.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanne-hathaway-career-fall-off-a-cliff-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnne%20Hathaway%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2043%2C%20says%20she%20decided%20not%20to%20go%20through%20life%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftry-worry-window-anxiety-productive-difference-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efeeling%20stressed%3C%2Fa%3E%20all%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20said%20she's%20been%20rethinking%20the%20way%20she%20handles%20pressure%2C%20particularly%20while%20leading%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-devil-wears-prada-sequel-release-date-actors-meryl-streep-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Devil%20Wears%20Prada%26quot%3B%20sequel%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20have%20a%20good%20time%20at%20a%20party%20if%20the%20hostess%20is%20stressed%20or%20she's%20letting%20her%20stress%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20Hathaway%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.harpersbazaar.com%2Fculture%2Ffilm-tv%2Fa70726276%2Fanne-hathaway-the-devil-wears-prada-2-interview-2026%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarper's%20Bazaar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20decided%20that%20it%20wasn't%20fair%20for%20me%20to%20move%20through%20my%20life%20as%20a%20stressed%20person.%20I%20don't%20want%20my%20kids%20to%20be%20around%20it%2C%20I%20don't%20want%20my%20friends%20to%20be%20around%20it%2C%20I%20don't%20want%20strangers%20to%20be%20around%20it%2C%20I%20don't%20want%20people%20I%20work%20with%20to%20be%20around%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHathaway%20said%20she's%20%26quot%3Bdone%20a%20lot%20of%20work%26quot%3B%20to%20process%20everything%20coming%20her%20way%20differently%2C%20so%20it%20feels%20exciting%20rather%20than%20overwhelming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20she%20sees%20her%20career%20in%20two%20phases%3A%20an%20earlier%20chapter%20that%20left%20little%20room%20for%20anything%20outside%20work%2C%20and%20a%20second%20chapter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkeira-knightley-work-life-balance-career-advice-parenting-motherhood-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshaped%20by%20parenthood%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sobriety%2C%20and%20being%20more%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%2C%20there%20was%20this%20focus%20that%20was%20really%20uncompromising%20and%20uninterrupted%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20just%20can't%20tell%20you%20anymore%20what%20life%20is%20like%20without%20kids%2C%20but%20kids%20interrupt%20you%20all%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20she%20no%20longer%20tries%20to%20keep%20everything%20perfectly%20in%20sync%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20friends%20and%20I%20talk%20about%20it%20a%20lot%2C%20and%20we%20actually%20feel%20very%20defeated%20by%20the%20concept%20of%20balance%2C%26quot%3B%20Hathaway%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20weight%20shifts%20in%20one%20direction%2C%20you%20then%20have%20to%20bounce%20it%20up%20on%20the%20other%20side%2C%20and%20we%20find%20that%20it%20winds%20us%20up%20as%20opposed%20to%20making%20us%20steady.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20like%2C%20'We%20seek%20to%20harmonize%20our%20life.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHathaway%20isn't%20the%20only%20high-profile%20parent%20rethinking%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freese-witherspoon-parenting-motherhood-exhausting-hollywood-work-life-balance-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EReese%20Witherspoon%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20said%20raising%20her%20older%20children%20taught%20her%20what's%20not%20worth%20stressing%20over%20as%20she%20parents%20her%20youngest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20parenting%20for%2025%20years.%20I%20also%20feel%20very%20comfortable%20that%20I%20know%20the%20little%20things%20that%20aren't%20as%20important.%20Like%20I%20had%20a%20friend%20say%2C%20'I'm%20not%20there%20for%20pickup.%20And%20is%20that%20OK%3F'%20Absolutely.%20You%20know%2C%20you%20can't%20be%20at%20every%20soccer%20game%2C%20every%20morning%20meeting%2C%20pick%20up%2C%20drop%20off%2C%20make%20the%20lunch%2C%20do%20the%20volunteer%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20Witherspoon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGrey's%20Anatomy%26quot%3B%20star%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreys-anatomy-camilla-luddington-balance-work-kids-motherhood-parenting-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECamilla%20Luddington%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20said%20that%20juggling%20work%20and%20kids%20doesn't%20come%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20take%20the%20pressure%20off%2C%20I'll%20be%20like%2C%20'You%20know%20what%3F%20Today%20I'm%20probably%20going%20to%20be%20better%20at%20my%20job%20than%20I%20am%20at%20parenting%20because%20I'm%20on%20set%20all%20day.%20But%20tomorrow%20I'm%20off%20and%20I%20can%20be%20a%20better%20parent%2C'%26quot%3B%20Luddington%20said.%20%26quot%3BLetting%20go%20of%20that%20need%20to%20be%20perfectly%20balanced%20all%20the%20time%20has%20been%20very%20freeing%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanne-hathaway-quit-being-stressed-mother-kids-parenting-career-balance-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774840808000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c9d965f573a637a75674b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanne-hathaway-quit-being-stressed-mother-kids-parenting-career-balance-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anne%20Hathaway%20said%20she's%20learning%20to%20approach%20work%20differently%20so%20it%20feels%20more%20exciting%20than%20overwhelming.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22agoh%40businessinsider.com%20