id%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20told%20the%20FT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20we%20take%20Kharg%20Island%2C%20maybe%20we%20don't.%20We%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20options%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20told%20the%20FT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20that%20would%20mean%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20had%20to%20be%20there%20for%20a%20while.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fak2Zm%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Line%20chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fak2Zm%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EOil%20prices%20have%20surged%20since%20the%20US%20and%20Israel%20began%20bombing%20Iran%20at%20the%20end%20of%20February%2C%20and%20Iran%20retaliated%20by%20essentially%20closing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-strikes-middle-east-shipping-air-cargo-freight-impact-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStrait%20of%20Hormuz.%3C%2Fa%3E%20About%2020%25%20of%20the%20world's%20oil%20supply%20and%20liquified%20natural%20gas%20passes%20through%20the%20waterway%20off%20Iran's%20coast.%20Major%20oil%20hubs%20across%20the%20Middle%20East%20have%20also%20been%20damaged%20during%20the%20conflict%2C%20further%20straining%20the%20global%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20recently%2C%20the%20Houthis%20launched%20two%20missile%20and%20drone%20attacks%20at%20Israel%20over%20the%20weekend.%20Yahya%20Saree%2C%20the%20spokesman%20for%20the%20Yemeni%20Armed%20Forces%2C%20confirmed%20the%20attacks%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20American%20consumers%2C%20this%20all%20translates%20to%20higher%20gas%20prices.%20The%20national%20average%20in%20the%20US%20was%20%243.98%20on%20Sunday%2C%20up%20from%20%242.98%20in%20February.%20The%20International%20Energy%20Agency%20has%20released%20400%20million%20barrels%20of%20oil%20from%20a%20strategic%20reserve%20to%20ease%20economic%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgas-prices-oil-iran-energy-chris-wright-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20Energy%20Secretary%20Chris%20Wright%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20on%20March%208%20the%20war%20wouldn't%20be%20%26quot%3Blong-term%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Trump%20administration%20and%20Iranian%20officials%20have%20not%20yet%20signaled%20an%20exit%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20The%20Washington%20Post%20reported%20that%20the%20Pentagon%20is%20preparing%20for%20weeks%20of%20ground%20operations%20in%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20developments%20over%20the%20weekend%20weighed%20on%20the%20stock%20markets%2C%20with%20Asian%20markets%20kicking%20off%20Monday%20in%20the%20red.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJapan's%20Nikkei%20225%20and%20South%20Korea's%20Kospi%20indexes%20both%20lost%20over%205%25.%20Hong%20Kong's%20Hang%20Seng%20Index%20was%20down%20about%202%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20are%20now%20focused%20on%20the%20escalating%20conflict%20rather%20than%20on%20diplomatic%20efforts%2C%20Chris%20Weston%2C%20the%20head%20of%20research%20at%20Pepperstone%2C%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20market%20is%20now%20reacting%20to%20higher%20crude%20pricing%20and%20towards%20the%20fallout%20in%20the%20economic%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20Weston%20wrote%2C%20pointing%20to%20expectations%20of%20short-term%20inflation%2C%20interest%20rate%20volatility%2C%20and%20energy%20supply%20shortages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-rise-iran-war-brent-wti-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774837615000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c9a40df573a637a7567469%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-rise-iran-war-brent-wti-2026-