re%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENatalie%20Chiu%20grew%20up%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20moved%20to%20the%20UK%20to%20study%20food%20science.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHer%20alcohol%20intolerance%20led%20her%20and%20her%20now-husband%20to%20start%20a%20sparkling%20tea%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELast%20year%2C%20she%20handed%20in%20her%20notice%20at%20her%20day%20job%20to%20focus%20on%20her%20business%20full-time.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Natalie%20Chiu%2C%2036%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20Saicho.%20Her%20words%20have%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20liked%20going%20out%20for%20good%20food%2C%20but%20when%20wine%20pairings%20were%20involved%2C%20I%20felt%20second-class%20because%20of%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-unusual-approach-alcohol-forcing-bars-change-menu-strategy-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ealcohol%20intolerance%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20order%20juice%20or%20a%20glass%20of%20water%20instead.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20missing%20out%20on%20a%20big%20part%20of%20that%20dining%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20changed%20when%20I%20met%20my%20husband%2C%20Charlie.%20For%20our%20first%20date%2C%20we%20celebrated%20our%20birthdays%20together%20at%20a%20fine-dining%20restaurant%20in%20London.%20He%20loves%20having%20drinks%2C%20so%20I%20wanted%20to%20give%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-wines-to-serve-guests-certified-sommelier-keeps-on-hand-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewine%20pairings%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20second%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20couldn't%20even%20finish%20the%20first%20glass%20because%20my%20face%20was%20already%20so%20red.%20I%20felt%20embarrassed%20about%20having%20to%20push%20myself%20into%20doing%20something%20I%20wasn't%20comfortable%20with%20just%20to%20feel%20included.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomething%20triggered%20me%20after%20that%20first%20date.%20I%20realized%20that%20there%20must%20be%20something%20I%20could%20do.%20That%20was%20how%20the%20idea%20for%20Saicho%2C%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flife-coach-jay-shetty-tea-empire-with-joyo-and-sama-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esparkling%20tea%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Natalie%20Chiu%20in%20a%20cap%20and%20gown%20with%20her%20family%20after%20graduating.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b78bd94d65ec51752a0a68%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChiu's%20dad%20introduced%20her%20to%20the%20role%20of%20a%20flavorist%20%E2%80%94%20she%20moved%20to%20the%20UK%20to%20study%20food%20science.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Natalie%20Chiu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229f7c276c-e5b2-40f4-8095-543831f89a67%5C%22%3EBalancing%20school%2C%20work%2C%20and%20my%20own%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flindsay-jang-entrepreneur-mom-finding-work-life-balance-hong-kong-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egrew%20up%20in%20Hong%20Kong%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20dad%20worked%20in%20the%20fragrance%20industry%2C%20and%20he%20would%20bring%20home%20perfume%20samples.%20It%20piqued%20my%20curiosity%20from%20an%20early%20age.%20I%20was%20invested%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20creating%20something%20for%20someone%20to%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20my%20dad%20introduced%20me%20to%20the%20role%20of%20a%20flavorist.%20Through%20our%20conversations%2C%20I%20became%20interested%20in%20creating%20flavors%20and%20learning%20about%20how%20we%20interact%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20at%2018%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20the%20UK%20to%20study%20food%20science.%20Staying%20there%20long-term%20was%20never%20on%20my%20mind.%20I%20planned%20to%20complete%20my%20studies%20and%20go