%20take%20the%20chance.%20Since%20we'd%20already%20had%20a%20gradual%20start%2C%20the%20transition%20was%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20couple%20is%20visiting%20Hojicha%20tea%20production%20in%20Shizuoka.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b78d4c4d65ec51752a0a6c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20tested%20different%20varieties%20of%20tea%20from%20around%20the%20world.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Natalie%20Chiu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222f0b3b83-6c56-4949-9046-01568093f91c%5C%22%3EPartners%20in%20business%20and%20in%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20very%20different%20personalities.%20But%20we're%20also%20both%20scientists%2C%20so%20we%20embrace%20different%20ways%20of%20thinking.%20It%20worked%20really%20well%20for%20the%20two%20of%20us%20as%20partners%20and%20eventually%2C%20co-owners%20because%20we%20know%20each%20other's%20strengths%20and%20weaknesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarried-couple-quit-jobs-open-whiskey-distillery-start-family-business-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EManaging%20the%20company%20together%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20strengthened%20our%20relationship.%20We%20can%20better%20understand%20each%20other's%20pressures%20because%20we%20share%20experiences.%20It's%20really%20difficult%20not%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20business%2C%20but%20as%20long%20as%20we're%20both%20willing%20to%20discuss%20it%2C%20it%20makes%20for%20a%20healthy%20relationship.%20We're%20able%20to%20solve%20things%20much%20quicker%20that%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20personal%20and%20working%20lives%20will%20always%20be%20intertwined%2C%20and%20we're%20both%20happy%20with%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Couple%20tasting%20sparkling%20drinks%20in%20Taiwan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20