%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20people%2060%20and%20over%20is%20expected%20to%20rise%20from%201%20billion%20in%202020%20to%201.4%20billion%20by%202030.%20By%202050%2C%20that%20figure%20will%20double%20to%202.1%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews-room%2Ffact-sheets%2Fdetail%2Fageing-and-health%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWHO%20projections%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20statistics%20don't%20capture%20what%20aging%20can%20look%20like%20in%20real%20life%20%E2%80%94%20like%20watching%20an%2086-year-old%20man%20swing%20himself%20over%20a%20pull-up%20bar%20at%20a%20public%20fitness%20corner%20in%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20collection%20is%20part%20of%20our%3Cstrong%3E%20Still%20Going%20Strong%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eseries%2C%20which%20spotlights%20people%20in%20their%2070s%20and%20beyond%20who've%20built%20routines%2C%20communities%2C%20or%20groups%20to%20stay%20active.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20over%2070%20and%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20aging%20well%2C%20email%20this%20reporter%20at%20agoh%40businessinsider.com.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20keep%20count%20of%20his%20flips%20on%20the%20bar%2C%20but%20somewhere%20along%20the%20way%2C%20I%20lose%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20minutes%20later%2C%20Peng%20Lin%20Hua%20finishes%20his%20set%20and%20walks%20toward%20me%20with%20barely%20a%20trace%20of%20sweat%20on%20his%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20tells%20me%20he%20started%20practicing%20headstands%20with%20his%20wife%20in%20his%2050s.%20Later%2C%20he%20offers%20to%20demonstrate.%20He%20bends%20down%2C%20plants%20his%20hands%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20slowly%20lifts%20his%20body%20until%20he's%20upside%20down%2C%20legs%20extended%20toward%20the%20sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeng%20is%20one%20of%20four%20older%20men%2C%20aged%20between%2076%20and%2085%2C%20who%20call%20themselves%20Team%20Strong%20Silvers.%20They%20are%20united%20by%20their%20discipline%3A%20They%20work%20out%20almost%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cs%3EI%3C%2Fs%3En%20Singapore%2C%20preparing%20for%20an%20aging%20population%20has%20become%20a%20matter%20of%20policy%20as%20much%20as%20personal%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20has%20launched%20national%20campaigns%20encouraging%20older%20adults%20to%20remain%20physically%20and%20socially%20engaged.%20In%20July%2C%20the%20Asian%20nation%20is%20set%20to%20raise%20its%20retirement%20age%20by%20a%20year%20to%2064.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20men%20didn't%20set%20out%20to%20form%20a%20team.%20Over%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20a%20senior%20gym%20had%20just%20opened%20at%20a%20neighborhood%20community%20center%2C%20but%20few%20residents%20were%20using%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobert%20Ho%2C%20who%20managed%20the%20center's%20active%20aging%20and%20wellness%20initiatives%20at%20the%20time%2C%20wanted%20to%20encourage%20more%20seniors%20to%20use%20the%20gym.%20So%20he%20brought%20in%20a%20few%20older%20volunteers%20who%20were%20already%20active%20to%20run%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fcalisthenics%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecalisthenics%20sessions%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20to%20show%20people%20that%20even%20though%20they're%20older%2C%20they%20can%20still%20do%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Ho%2C%2056%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20local%20media%20took%20notice%2C%20the%20informal%20group%20gradually%20evolved%20into%20what%20is%20now%20known%20as%20Team%20Strong%20Silvers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHo%2C%20now%20a%20program%20executive%20at%20Fei%20Yue%20Community%20Services%20in%20Singapore%2C%20still%20manages%20the%20group's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fteamstrongsilvers%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%20account%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20organization%20is%20also%20where%20the%20four%20men%20now%20volunteer%2C%20demonstrating%20exercises%20and%20inspiring%20other%20older%20adults%20to%20keep%20moving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20glimpse%20of%20how%20one%20country%20is%20adapting%20to%20an%20aging%20population%20%E2%80%94%20a%20challenge%20that%20extends%20far%20beyond%20its%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20and%20more%20Americans%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-we-learned-from-americas-oldest-workers-80-over-80-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworking%20past%20traditional%20retirement%20age%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20longevity%20has%20become%20big%20business%2C%20fueling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanti-aging-longevity-trends-shock-testosterone-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebiohacking%20trends%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20even%20tech-backed%20life-extension%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20adding%20years%20is%20only%20part%20of%20the%20story.%20What%20those%20extra%20years%20can%20look%20like%20is%20just%20as%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20stories%20below%2C%20you'll%20meet%20each%20member%20of%20Team%20Strong%20Silvers%20in%20his%20own%20words.%20None%20of%20them%20is%20interested%20in%20slowing%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthy-aging-singapore-longevity-fitness-wellness-team-strong-silvers-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774829461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ae5892168b545ac9a6bc75%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthy-aging-singapore-longevity-fitness-wellness-team-strong-silvers-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20men%20in%20their%2070s%20and%2080s%20can%20do%20pull-ups%2C%20splits%2C%20and%20headstands.%20They%20call%20themselves%20Team%20Strong%20Silvers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22agoh%40businessinsider.com%20(Amanda%20Goh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthy-aging-singapore-longevity-fitness-