ved%20to%20Austin%2C%20Texas%2C%20to%20live%20around%20other%20creators%20and%20streamers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20high%20earner%20on%20OnlyFans%20helped%20me%20get%20the%20O-1B%20visa%2C%20something%20I%20probably%20couldn't%20have%20done%20if%20I%20were%20just%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwitch-ceo-dan-clancy-profitability-livestreaming-future-under-amazon-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETwitch%20streamer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c559d509-bf79-4826-bd7f-3cce939e47da%5C%22%3EHow%20I%20got%20into%20OnlyFans%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%20considered%20going%20into%20OnlyFans%20or%20sex%20work.%20But%20in%202021%2C%20my%20mom%20was%20really%20sick%20while%20working%20really%20hard%20in%20Colombia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20year%2C%20OnlyFans%20reached%20out%20to%20me%20because%20I%20had%20a%20large%20Twitch%20following%2C%20about%20a%20million%20followers%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarning%20money%20on%20OnlyFans%20isn't%20straightforward.%20This%20is%20something%20people%20don't%20really%20understand%2C%20because%20they%20see%20OnlyFans%20creators%20broadcasting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonlyfans-creators-how-they-made-1-million-on-the-platform-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elavish%20lifestyles%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20always%20tell%20people%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20following%2C%20you%20are%20not%20going%20to%20make%20money%20on%20the%20platform.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20very%20lucrative.%20The%20gig%20allowed%20me%20to%20help%20my%20mom%20retire%20and%20find%20an%20apartment%20in%20Colombia%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20taking%20care%20of%20her%20ever%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228fe49319-858c-4ad4-bba2-1bc523f936aa%5C%22%3EGetting%20the%20O-1B%20visa%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-einstein-o1-visa-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EO-1B%20visa%3C%2Fa%3E%20first%20in%202022%20and%20had%20it%20renewed%20in%202025%2C%20which%20is%20valid%20until%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20process%20has%20not%20been%20cheap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20to%20shell%20out%20between%20%2450%2C000%20and%20%2475%2C000%20on%20lawyer%20fees%20and%20application%20for%20visas.%20Just%20to%20get%20the%20visa%20expedited%20cost%20thousands%2C%20as%20it%20would've%20taken%20me%20years%20to%20get%20it%20approved%20if%20I%20did%20not%20get%20it%20expedited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would've%20never%20been%20able%20to%20afford%20to%20pay%20all%20these%20lawyer%20fees%20if%20I%20didn't%20have%20OnlyFans.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff6f0544-8df0-48df-b10b-0e23806f1737%5C%22%3EBeing%20in%20the%20US%20boosted%20my%20career%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20visa%20application%2C%20I%20had%20to%20show%20that%20I%20was%20collaborating%20with%20influencers%20in%20the%20US.%20This%20was%20actually%20one%20of%20my%20main%20motivations%20for%20moving%20to%20this%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20that%20moving%20would%20benefit%20my%20career.%20The%20amount%20of%20exposure%20that%20you%20get%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-making-money-as-influencer-has-changed-in-a-decade-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einfluencer%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20being%20with%20other%20influencers%20is%20huge.%20I%20live%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Austin%2C%20where%20there's%20a%20big%20group%20of%20influencers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EContent%20creators%20are%20looking%20to%20connect%20with%20other%20creators%20and%20collaborate.%20For%2012%20years%20in%20Canada%2C%20I%20did%20it%20all%20by%20myself%20and%20didn't%20have%20anyone%20that%20I%20could%20confide%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20deal%20with%20so%20many%20things%20no%20one%20else%20can%20understand%2C%20like%20stalkers%2C%20constant%20criticism%2C%20and%20being%20bombarded%20with%20people's%20opinions%20about%20you.%20So%20it's%20nice%20to%20have%20a%20community%20that%20relates%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20another%20reason%20I%20like%20working%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20US%20doesn't%20diminish%20my%20work.%20In%20the%20O-1%20B%20visa%20application%2C%20I%20just%20had%20to%20show%20that%20I'm%20successful%20in%20my%20field%2C%20regardless%20of%20what%20that%20field%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20really%20know%20if%20I%20want%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20US%20forever.%20I%20know%20for%20sure%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20grow%20old%20here%20and%20pay%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-soaring-healthcare-costs-are-changing-where-millionaires-move-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emedical%20bills%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US.%20But%20I%20see%20myself%20working%20and%20building%20out%20my%20career%20here%20for%20another%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20negative%20connotation%20to%20being%20an%20OnlyFans%20creator%2C%20but%20I%20do%20not%20have%20any%20regrets%20about%20it.%20If%20I%20had%20to%20do%20it%20all%20over%20again%2C%20I%20would%20do%20it%20exactly%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonlyfans-model-twitch-streamer-extraordinary-artist-visa-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774829281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6968744364858d02d2186447%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonlyfans-model-twitch-streamer-extraordinary-artist-visa-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Natalia%20Mogollon%20is%20a%20Twitch%20streamer%20and%20OnlyFans%20model%20with%20an%20O-1%20B%20visa.%20Staying%20in%20the%20US%20has%20given%20her%20community%2C%20dignity%2C%20and%20a%20career%20boost.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abharade%40insider.com%20(Aditi%20Bharade)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonlyfans-model-twitch-streamer-extraor