imminent%20threat%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20alleged%20nuclear%20weapons%20program%2C%20and%20its%20proxies%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20like%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon%20and%20the%20Houthis%20in%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIran%2C%20however%2C%20has%20shown%20resilience.%20How%20long%20the%20war%20lasts%20will%20likely%20depend%20on%20how%20long%20the%20world%20can%20withstand%20its%20economic%20impact.%20Here%20are%20some%20of%20the%20major%20ways%20that%20impact%20is%20spreading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20oil%20shock%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227097%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gasoline%20drips%20from%20the%20tip%20of%20a%20gas%20station%20nozzle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c98deb8373a547629c76d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224731%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGasoline%20drips%20from%20a%20gas%20station%20nozzle.%20The%20US%20and%20Israeli%20war%20on%20Iran%20has%20disrupted%20oil%20supplies%2C%20sending%20the%20price%20of%20oil%20skyrocketing%20past%20%24100%20a%20barrel%20and%20forcing%20some%20countries%20to%20ration%20supplies.%3Cp%3EAlain%20JOCARD%20%2F%20AFP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGlobal%20oil%20prices%20have%20skyrocketed%20since%20the%20military%20conflict%20began%20in%20late%20February%2C%20mainly%20due%20to%20the%20near-closure%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-invest-straight-of-hormuz-crisis-stocks-bonds-treasurys-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStrait%20of%20Hormuz%3C%2Fa%3E.%20About%2020%25%20of%20the%20world's%20oil%20supply%20and%20liquefied%20natural%20gas%20pass%20through%20the%20waterway%20off%20Iran's%20coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20major%20oil%20hubs%20across%20the%20Middle%20East%20have%20also%20sustained%20damage%2C%20including%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-fire-key-uae-oil-hub-after-intercepted-drone-atta