8k%20changed%20his%20tune%2C%20turning%20optimistic%20that%20the%20economy%20had%20improved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20month%20later%2C%20Trump%20bombed%20Iran%2C%20surprising%20the%20world%20and%20putting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstagflation-us-economy-outlook-oil-prices-inflation-shock-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estagflation%20back%20on%20the%20table%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20driven%20this%20time%20by%20the%20potential%20for%20the%20rising%20cost%20of%20oil%20to%20trigger%20inflation.%20The%20last%20time%20stagflation%20took%20hold%2C%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20it%20was%20also%20driven%20by%20the%20price%20of%20oil.%20It%20devastated%20the%20US%20economy%2C%20lowered%20living%20standards%2C%20and%20triggered%20intense%20financial%20pressure%20on%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstagflation-economy-outlook-2026-stock-market-fed-rate-cuts-inflation-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EStagflation%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20often%20considered%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-panic-sp500-tariffs-rally-bull-market-stagflation-economy-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eworst-case%20scenario%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20economy%20since%20it's%20difficult%20to%20resolve.%20The%20Federal%20Reserve%20would%20be%20restricted%20in%20its%20ability%20to%20cut%20rates%20to%20ease%20a%20recession%2C%20because%20it%20would%20risk%20stoking%20even%20more%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20Reserve%20Chairman%20Jerome%20Powell%20waved%20off%20the%20threat%20of%20stagflation%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20earlier%20this%20month.%20Powell%20said%20the%20current%20economic%20climate%20was%20difficult%2C%20but%20didn't%20think%20it%20was%20comparable%20to%20the%201970s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEconomist%20Paul%20Krugman%2C%20however%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstagflation-paul-krugman-inflation-economy-policy-jerome-powell-trump-iran-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eisn't%20so%20sure%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAir%20travel%20chaos%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227008%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20phone%20shows%20flights%20avoiding%20airspace%20over%20Iran%20on%20a%20flight-tracking%20app.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c992138e5f53c45ea2d3a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Iran%20war%20has%20forced%20airlines%20to%20reroute%20or%20cancel%20flights%20all%20over%20the%20Middle%20East.%3Cp%3EMarcin%20Golba%2FNurPhoto%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20industry%20felt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrikes-on-iran-flights-canceled-diverted-busiest-airspace-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20war's%20reverberations%3C%2Fa%3E%20immediately.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirspace%20closures%20in%20the%20region%20forced%20airlines%20to%20reroute%20or%20cancel%20flights%2C%20leaving%20tourists%20marooned.%20Dubai%20International%20has%20gradually%20resumed%20operations%20for%20some%20flights%2C%20but%20many%20airports%20have%20either%20limited%20operations%20or%20suspended%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20US%20embassies%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20are%20also%20closed%2C%20leaving%20large%20swaths%20of%20travelers%20stranded%20without%20a%20clear%20way%20home.%20One%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-stranded-middle-east-government-frustration-embassy-closed-iran-war-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20visiting%20Dubai%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20the%20war%20broke%20out%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20felt%20%26quot%3Bbetrayed%20and%20left%20out%20to%20dry%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20government's%20lack%20of%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20UAE%20said%20it%20would%20bear%20%26quot%3Ball%20hosting%20and%20accommodation%20costs%20for%20affected%20and%20stranded%20passengers%2C%26quot%3B%20some%20tourists%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiddle-east-travel-disruption-hotel-bills-expenses-vouchers-who-pays-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eracked%20up%20thousands%20of%20dollars%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20additional%20costs%20while%20waiting%20to%20book%20a%20ticket%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%20jet%20fuel%20prices%20are%20skyrocketing%2C%20making%20plane%20tickets%20more%20expensive.%20Jet%20fuel%20reached%20an%20average%20of%20%24197%20a%20barrel%20on%20March%2020%2C%20according%20to%20the%20International%20Air%20Transport%20Association.%20The%20price%20was%20%2499%20at%20the%20end%20of%20February.%20Some%20airlines%20%E2%80%94%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairlines-raise-prices-cancel-flights-due-to-fuel-costs-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQantas%20and%20Air%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20are%20raising%20ticket%20prices%20and%20passing%20the%20costs%20on%20to%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESupply%20chain%20disruptions%20come%20for%20AI%20and%20the%20price%20of%20food%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FssGbC%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Line%20chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FssGbC%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20supply%20of%20oil%20gets%20most%20of%20the%20headlines.%20There%20are%20other%20commodities%2C%20however%2C%20that%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodity-market-impact-disruptions-iran-war-sulfur-fertilizer-helium-inflation-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efacing%20supply%20chain%20disruptions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20those%20commodities%20will%20affect%20everything%20from%20the%20AI%20revolution%20to%20food%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESulfur%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20is%20a%20byproduct%20of%20oil%20and%20gas%20processing.%20It's%20wisely%20recycled%20to%20help%20extract%20metals%20like%20copper%20and%20lithium.%20Those%20metals%20are%20in%20high%20demand%20as%20AI%20companies%20race%20to%20build%20data%20centers%20to%20power%20their%20products.%20They%20are%20also%20used%20in%20the%20production%20of%20electric%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESulfur%20is%20also%20key%20to%20producing%20urea%2C%20a%20widely%20used%20specialized%20fertilizer.%20A%20third%20of%20the%20global%20fertilizer%20supply%20also%20passes%20through%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz.%20The%20prolonged%20disruption%20to%20the%20fertilizer%20supply%20will%20force%20farmers%20to%20ration%20its%20use%2C%20resulting%20in%20lower%20crop%20yields%20and%2C%20ultimately%2C%20higher%20grocery%20prices%2C%20hitting%20the%20average%20consumer%20where%20it%20hurts%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20on%20Iran%20is%20also%20affecting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-price-spike-impact-electricity-power-ai-semiconductor-chips-fab-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20supply%20of%20helium%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Qatar%20supplies%20nearly%20one-third%20of%20the%20world's%20helium%2C%20a%20byproduct%20of%20liquid%20natural%20gas%20production%20that%20is%20critical%20for%20semiconductor%20manufacturing.%20That's%20another%20blow%20to%20AI%2C%20one%20of%20the%20key%20industries%20propping%20up%20the%20US%20economy.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt'll%20require%20a%20peace%20deal%20between%20the%20US%2C%20Israel%2C%20and%20Iran%20to%20resolve%20all%20these%20disruptions.%20For%20now%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-iran-peace-plan-markets-oil-prices-stocks-hormuz-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20deal%20remains%20elusive%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20