5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20one-bedroom%20signature%20suite%20at%20the%20Swan%20Reserve%20was%20quiet%20and%20spacious.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20run%20by%20Marriott%2C%20it%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20Disney%20perks%2C%20including%20bus%20and%20boat%20transportation%2C%20early%20entry%2C%20and%20an%20on-site%20Cast%20Member%20to%20help%20with%20all%20things%20Disney%20Parks.%20There's%20even%20complimentary%20childcare%20when%20dining%20at%20specific%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20beautiful%20walk%20to%20EPCOT%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-hollywood-studios-attractions-ranking-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHollywood%20Studios%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20rooms%20are%20huge%2C%20flooded%20with%20natural%20light%2C%20and%20pretty%20much%20Disney-theme%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20part%20is%20the%20lobby%20lounge%2C%20Stir.%20Anyone%20who%20has%20tried%20to%20find%20food%20or%20a%20relaxing%20cocktail%20after%20braving%20the%20post-fireworks%20crowd%20at%20Magic%20Kingdom%20knows%20how%20hard%20it%20can%20be%20to%20find%20late-night%20food%20at%20Disney.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20every%20night%2C%20we%20visited%20Stir%20for%20a%20snack%20and%20cocktails%20like%20the%20fruity%20and%20delicious%20Garden%20Party%20cocktail%20for%20me%2C%20and%20the%20whimsical%20Banana%20Hands%20for%20my%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227b90a976-5f9c-438b-97d8-0cf7dc15fa5f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20top%20priority%20was%20the%20Disney%20magic%20we%20love%2C%20the%20food%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20just%20four%20days%2C%20we%20ate%20at%2010%20different%20spots%20%E2%80%94%20artsy%20bites%20and%20sips%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-things-disney-world-after-going-over-30-times-one-year-2022%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEPCOT%20International%20Festival%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Arts%20Food%20Studios%2C%20brunch%20at%20Art%20Smith%20Homecomin'%2C%20dinner%20with%20stunning%20firework%20views%20at%20California%20Grill%2C%20and%20cocktails%20with%20pirates%20at%20The%20Beak%20and%20Barrel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20dining%20at%20The%20Beak%20and%20Barrel.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bc23aad387710cb9e46464%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20had%20prime%20seating%20in%20front%20of%20the%20fireplace%20at%20The%20Beak%20and%20Barrel.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20finally%20a%20lounge%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-magic-kingdom-attractions-ranking-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMagic%20Kingdom%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20needed%20an%20eyepatch%2C%20a%20parrot%2C%20and%20the%20lyrics%20to%20%26quot%3BYo%20Ho%26quot%3B%20memorized%20when%20stepping%20into%20the%20immersive%20world%20of%20The%20Beak%20and%20Barrel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20prime%20seating%20in%20front%20of%20the%20fireplace%20with%20battling%20ships-in-a-bottle%20above%20us.%20The%20Beak%20and%20Barrel%20is%20not%20a%20spot%20for%20lounging%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%20special%20effects%2C%20a%20two-drink%20limit%2C%20and%20a%20maximum%20of%2045%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ec6e094f-2c99-4a10-b3b8-4ef2d4a426c6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDinner%20at%20EPCOT's%20Takumi-Tei%20was%20elegant%2C%20and%20for%20guests%20ages%208%20and%20up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complete%20opposite%20of%20the%20noise%20and%20rushed%20feeling%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhagrids-magical-creatures-motorbike-adventure-review-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20Beak%20and%20Barrel%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20the%20tranquil%2C%20soothing%20Takumi-Tei%20at%20EPCOT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETakumi-Tei%20is%20tucked%20away%20in%20the%20Japan%20pavilion%20with%20subtle%20signs%20leading%20to%20the%20heavy%20wooden%20doors.%20Once%20inside%2C%20we%20were%20transported%20down%20a%20tranquil%20hallway%2C%20away%20from%20the%20hustle%20and%20bustle%20of%20EPCOT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22tableside%20tea%20service%20at%20Takumi-Tei%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bc23ecebc245a53a811e5f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20tableside%20tea%20service%20at%20Takumi-Tei%20is%20a%20highlight%20of%20the%20meal.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20five%20different%20dining%20rooms%2C%20and%20we%20were%20in%20the%20washi%20paper%20room.%20Pink%20cherry%20blossoms%2C%20softly%20lit%20from%20behind%2C%20lined%20the%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETakumi-Tei%20is%20omakase%20%E2%80%94%20or%20%26quot%3Bleave%20it%20up%20to%20the%20chef%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20style.%20There's%20no%20kids'%20menu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20dish%20was%20beautifully%20plated%2C%20and%20each%20course%20was%20creatively%20and%20carefully%20prepared.%20Our%20elegant%20and%20knowledgeable%20server%2C%20Sakura%2C%20was%20soft-spoken%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20tranquil%2C%20exquisite%20ambiance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2266e0abbc-72e8-403e-8387-f471f940008c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20visit%20to%20the%20adults-only%20GEO-82%20lounge%20was%20magical%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20World%20is%20adding%20more%20experiences%20for%20grown-ups%2C%20like%20the%20adult-exclusive%20EPCOT%20lounge%20GEO-82.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20no%20strollers%2C%20no%20kids'%20menu%2C%20and%20no%20lack-of-a-nap%20meltdowns.%20What%20it%20does%20have%20is%20sophisticated%20homages%20to%20Spaceship%20Earth%2C%20stunning%20views%2C%20a%20stellar%20cocktail%20menu%2C%20and%20delicious%20bites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20at%20Epcot%20restaurant%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bc268aebc245a53a811e7e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20favorite%20dining%20experience%20was%20GEO-82%2C%20an%20adults-only%20lounge%20at%20EPCOT.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20time%20limit%20at%20GEO-82.%20We%20relaxed%20and%20took%20in%20the%20details%20like%20the%20Spaceship%20Earth%20on%20the%20ice%20cube%20in%20the%20Brown%20Butter%20Old%20Fashioned.%20I%20took%20my%20time%20sipping%20my%20Peach%20Shrub%20Whisky%20Smash%2C%20savoring%20the%20accompanying%20cookie.%20The%20only%20cocktail%20that%20comes%20with%20a%20cookie!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cbd55b98-5669-44c1-93b7-22c732671ebb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20were%20out%20late%20every%20night%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20just%20the%20two%20of%20us%2C%20there%20was%20no%20one%20dragging%20behind%20and%20sighing.%20No%20one%20was%20falling%20apart%20because%20they%20were%20over-tired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223672%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Disney%20Starlight%20parade%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bc271debc245a53a811e83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20castle%20provides%20a%20stunning%20backdrop%20for%20the%2010%20p.m.%20Starlight%20parade.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20did%20late-night%20dinners%2C%20raced%20onto%20rides%20right%20before%20the%20park%20closed%2C%20and%20saw%20the%2010%20p.m.%20Disney%20Starlight%20nighttime%20parade.%20Cast%20Members%20directed%20us%20to%20one%20of%20the%20best%20spots%20to%20watch%20the%20parade%20%E2%80%94%20in%20Liberty%20Square%20near%20Ye%20Olde%20Christmas%20Shoppe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224cae0d76-f6b6-40ba-95e4-9b8f70b2a45f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20had%20the%20time%20to%20find%20magical%20Disney%20details%20I%20usually%20miss%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20walked%20right%20onto%20Star%20Tours%20and%20meandered%20slowly%20through%20the%20queue%20to%20warm%20up%20from%20the%20frigid%20mid-30s%20temps.%20Finding%20Disney%20easter%20eggs%20in%20the%20baggage%20screening%20area%20%E2%80%94%20like%20Genie's%20lamp%20and%20a%20Buzz%20Lightyear%20toy%20%E2%80%94%20were%20a%20bonus%20of%20taking%20our%20time%2C%20finding%20details%20we're%20usually%20rushing%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22easter%20eggs%20in%20the%20Star%20Tours%20queue%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bc2770d387710cb9e464aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20had%20time%20to%20find%20hidden%20details%20like%20easter%20eggs%20in%20the%20Star%20Tours%20queue.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20one%20to%20amuse%20while%20waiting%20in%20line%2C%20we%20made%20spontaneous%20attraction%20decisions.%20A%20pre-dinner%20journey%20on%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20Small%20World%26quot%3B%20was%20perfectly%20timed%2C%20and%20we%20were%20under%20the%20clock%20when%20it%20struck%207%20p.m.%20%E2%80%94%20a%20new%20experience%20for%20us%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20finally%20a%20Disney%20vacation%2C%20so%20I%20didn't%20make%20a%20ton%20of%20plans%2C%20book%20Lightning%20Lanes%2C%20or%20have%20a%20specific%20schedule%20for%20each%20day.%20We%20weren't%20rushing%20from%20one%20reservation%20to%20another%20or%20stalking%20the%20My%20Disney%20Experience%20App%20wait%20times.%20We%20lingered%20over%20meals%2C%20had%20new%20experiences%2C%20and%20enjoyed%20the%20magic%20our%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-world-without-kids-adult-trip-experience-