s%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fmiddle-east-crisis-mediators-gather-in-pakistan-for-talks-on-ending-month-long-iran-war%2Famp_articleshow%2F129881093.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fmiddle-east-crisis-mediators-gather-in-pakistan-for-talks-on-ending-month-long-iran-war%2Famp_articleshow%2F129881093.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20spent%20my%20life%20savings%20on%20a%20NYC%20deli%20that%20was%20infested%20with%20rodents.%20Now%2C%20I%20bring%20in%20up%20to%20%244%2C000%20a%20day%20thanks%20to%201%20viral%20sandwich.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joshua%20Dat%20outside%20of%20Datz%20Deli%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6efd0f573a637a756712a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJoshua%20Dat%20invested%20his%20life%20savings%20to%20open%20Datz%20Deli%20in%20Queens%20with%20his%20father.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20business%20struggled%20at%20first%20until%20Dat%20created%20the%20Mac%20Patty%20%E2%80%94%20a%20burger%20with%20mac%20and%20cheese.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDat's%20family%20now%20runs%20two%20successful%20Datz%20Deli%20locations%2C%20and%20he's%20looking%20to%20open%20a%20third.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Joshua%20Dat%2C%2033%2C%20owner%20of%20Datz%20Deli%20and%20creator%20of%20the%20Mac%20Patty%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20dad%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthird-generation-cafeteria-owner-wont-force-kids-run-family-business-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eamazing%20chef%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He'd%20been%20working%20in%20kitchens%20his%20whole%20life%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20like%20people%20never%20valued%20him%20the%20way%20they%20should%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20turned%2029%2C%20I%20took%20all%20the%20money%20I'd%20saved%20from%20age%2017%20and%20invested%20it%20in%20opening%20a%20store%20in%20Hollis%2C%20Queens%2C%20with%20him.%20We%20named%20it%20Datz%20Deli%20%E2%80%94%20now%20home%20of%20the%20famous%20Mac%20Patty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fje-taime-patisserie-going-viral-blessing-curse-small-business-bakery-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20struggle%20in%20the%20beginning%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20discovered%20the%20place%20was%20infested%20with%20rodents%20when%20I%20came%20in%20one%20morning%20and%20found%20half%20of%20my%20food%20supply%20eaten.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20those%20first%20few%20months%2C%20we%20were%20making%20about%20%24200%20to%20%24300%20a%20day%20%E2%80%94%20not%20enough%20to%20sustain%20the%20business.%20I%20thought%20I%20had%20messed%20up%2C%20and%20that%20all%20the%20money%20I%20had%20saved%20my%20whole%20life%20was%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20we%20have%20two%20shops%20%E2%80%94%20the%20original%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fqueens-global-food-tour-new-york-most-diverse-borough-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EQueens%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20another%20in%20Manhattan.%20Each%20brings%20in%20between%20%241%2C000%20to%20%244%2C000%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ba3d016d-0bbb-4e3e-8b89-92ba4a7c414b%5C%22%3EI%20started%20Datz%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20support%20my%20family%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221816%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joshua%20Dat%20in%20his%20deli%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6ecdc8e5f53c45ea2d072%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221218%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoshua%20Dat%20grew%20up%20without%20much.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20we%20didn't%20have%20much.%20After%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-cia-officer-john-kiriakou-how-secrecy-strained-marriage-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eparents%20divorced%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20I%20was%20young%2C%20it%20was%20mostly%20my%20mom%20supporting%20us%20four%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20go%20around%20the%20house%20and%20about%20town%20collecting%20loose%20change%20I%20could%20find%2C%20so%20I%20could%20give%20it%20to%20my%20mom%20when%20she'd%20cry%20about%20the%20water%20bill%20or%20the%20electricity%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20days%2C%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrowing-up-poor-homeless-help-make-better-parent-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estruggled%20to%20have%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Growing%20up%20like%20that%20is%20something%20you%20never%20want%20to%20go%20back%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20got%20older%2C%20I%20promised%20myself%20no%20one%20in%20my%20family%20would%20ever%20have%20to%20live%20like%20that%20again.%20Because%20of%20the%20business%2C%20they%20won't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e1aa9064-fb17-4d8e-9708-a3c138d3dc40%5C%22%3EThe%20Mac%20Patty%20changed%20everything%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202023%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222010%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Colorful%20mural%20on%20the%20side%20of%20Datz%20Deli%20showing%20the%20statue%20of%20liberty%20holding%20a%20mac%20patty.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6ed258e5f53c45ea2d074%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221230%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Statue%20of%20Liberty%20holds%20a%20Mac%20Patty%20on%20the%20side%20of%20Datz%20Deli.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20early%202023%2C%20we'd%20been%20open%20for%20a%20few%20months%2C%20and%20nothing%20was%20going%20right.%20I%20tried%20attracting%20customers%20with%20new%20creations%20like%20chopped%20cheeses%20on%20butter%20bread%20and%20roti%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrying-all-taco-bell-burritos-best-and-worst-review-photos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eburritos%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20nothing%20clicked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20one%20night%2C%20I%20was%20hungry%20for%20a%20beef%20patty%20with%20cheese%2C%20but%20we%20didn't%20have%20any%20cheese%20left%20because%20my%20dad%20had%20used%20it%20all%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmartha-stewart-one-pot-mac-and-cheese-recipe-20-minutes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emac%20and%20cheese%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222506%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tins%20of%20mac%20and%20cheese%20tacked%20atop%20each%20other%20at%20Datz%20Deli.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6f7a2f573a637a756715d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221546%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDatz%20Deli's%20mac%20and%20cheese.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20put%20the%20mac%20and%20cheese%20in%20the%20patty%2C%20cut%20it%20in%20half%2C%20looked%20at%20it%2C%20and%20just%20had%20a%20feeling%20this%20was%20it.%20This%20was%20going%20to%20go%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20little%20sister%20posted%20a%20pic%20of%20it%20on%20Instagram.%20The%20next%20morning%2C%20people%20came%20into%20the%20store%20asking%20for%20it.%20Soon%2C%20we%20had%20lines%20out%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mac%20Patty%20wasn't%20like%20anything%20else%20we%20had%20tried%20before.%20That%20gave%20me%20the%20confidence%20to%20keep%20building%20around%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221622%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Close%20up%20of%20a%20Mac%20Patty%20on%20white%20bread.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6edb68e5f53c45ea2d082%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221104%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDat%20has%20variations%20of%20the%20Mac%20Patty%2C%20like%20one%20with%20oxtail%20sauce%20on%20top.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffood-influencer-side-hustle-full-time-job-cookbook-royale-eats-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epaying%20influencers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20visit%20the%20store%20and%20promote%20it.%20Now%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20pay%20anyone%3B%20the%20store%20has%20gained%20its%20own%20reputation%2C%20and%20I%20was%20able%20to%20open%20the%20second%20shop%20in%20Manhattan%20from%20our%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f31a5bf5-9f46-4fd7-b7cd-ff7c6747c699%5C%22%3EI%20couldn't%20have%20done%20it%20without%20my%20family%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mom%20quit%20her%20full-time%20job%20in%20bill%20collecting%20to%20come%20help%20with%20the%20business.%20She%2C%20my%20father%2C%20and%20my%20older%20brother%20run%20the%20shop%20in%20Manhattan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20little%20sister%20and%20uncle%20run%20the%20shop%20in%20Queens%2C%20and%20I%20help%20out%20with%20online%20content%20and%20whatever%20else%20they%20need%20me%20for.%20I%20remember%20walking%20my%20little%20sis%20to%20school%2C%20and%20now%20to%20watch%20her%20help%20run%20this%20business%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20crazy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joshua%20Dat%20standing%20next%20to%20his%20mom%20in%20Datz%20Deli.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6f0538373a547629c73f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoshua%20Dat%20(left)%20with%20his%20mom%20(right)%20inside%20their%20deli.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20every%20day%20with%20your%20family%20is%20like%20what%20you%20might%20expect%20%E2%80%94%20terrible.%20We%20can%20fight%20like%20it's%20World%20War%20III%2C%20but%20we%20know%20that%20no%20matter%20what%20is%20said%20or%20what%20happens%2C%20we're%20all%20showing%20back%20up%20at%20the%20gate%20tomorrow%20to%20open%20the%20shops%20because%20we're%20all%20so%20proud%20of%20what%20it's%20become.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mother%20taught%20us%20growing%20up%20that%20you%20need%20people%20who'll%20never%20give%20up%20on%20you%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20hard%20it%20gets.%20And%20that's%20what%20we%20are%20for%20each%20other.%20Nothing%20breaks%20us%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20like%20to%20say%20that%20I%20started%20this%20business%2C%20but%20it's%20my%20family%20that%20keeps%20it%20going.%20Once%20we%20started%20seeing%20success%2C%20they%20really%20showed%20up%20for%20me%20at%20times%20when%20I%20didn't%20even%20want%20to%20show%20up%20for%20myself.%20And%20I'm%20so%20grateful%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20we're%20looking%20to%20open%20a%20location%20in%20Orlando%20%E2%80%94%20and%20my%20older%20sister%20will%20run%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnyc-deli-infested-viral-mac-patty-saved-business-datz-deli-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774788901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6efdd8e5f53c45ea2d096%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnyc-deli-infested-viral-mac-patty-saved-business-datz-deli-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Joshua%20Dat%20bought%20a%20deli%20in%20Queens%20to%20support%20his%20family%2C%20not%20knowing%20it%20was%20infested.%20The%20business%20struggled%20at%20first%20but%20later%20found%20huge%20success.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jorwig%40businessinsider.com%20(Jessica%20Orwig)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnyc-deli-infested-viral-mac-patty-saved-business-datz-deli-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20son%20is%20studying%20abroad%20in%20Spain%20this%20year.%20I'm%20trying%20to%20let%20go%2C%20but%20it's%20harder%20than%20I%20expected.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22706%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lisa%20white%20and%20her%20son%20in%20a%20graduation%20gown%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c56c57732a02451471382d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22530%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20is%20already%20grieving%20her%20son's%20absence%20as%20he%20prepares%20to%20study%20abroad.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lisa%20White%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20son%20leaves%20for%20his%20study%20abroad%20program%20in%20the%20fall%2C%20and%20I'm%20already%20grieving%20his%20absence.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20learning%20that%20letting%20go%20is%20a%20slow%20process%2C%20as%20I%20watch%20him%20prepare%20to%20go%20out%20on%20his%20own.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20have%20to%20trust%20that%20I've%20taught%20him%20everything%20and%20that%20I'm%20here%20if%20he%20needs%20me.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20few%20months%2C%20I%20will%20watch%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteen-got-first-job-how-to-budget-paycheck-save-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E18-year-old%20kid%3C%2Fa%3E%20walk%20away%20to%20start%20a%20life%20of%20his%20own%20in%20another%20country.%20I%20can%20already%20picture%20it%3A%20the%20way%20I'll%20stand%20there%20a%20little%20longer%20than%20necessary%2C%20trying%20to%20hold%20onto%20a%20moment%20that's%20already%20passing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20that%20later%2C%20I'll%20return%20to%20our%20apartment%20and%20feel%20the%20quiet%20in%20a%20way%20I%20haven't%20before.%20Not%20because%20it's%20empty%2C%20but%20because%20something%20has%20shifted.%20A%20chapter%20that%20once%20defined%20my%20daily%20life%20will%20have%20closed%2C%20whether%20I'm%20ready%20for%20it%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20my%20son%20leaves%20for%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-college-students-study-abroad-struggle-tuition-prices-trump-travel-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%20abroad%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Spain%20this%20fall%2C%20we're%20still%20moving%20through%20our%20routines.%20He's%20asking%20me%20questions%20about%20living%20on%20his%20own.%20We%20still%20have%20this%20time%20to%20share%20meals%2C%20routines%2C%20and%20small%20daily%20conversations.%20But%20everything%20feels%20different%20now.%20I%20know%20it%20won't%20last%20in%20the%20same%20way.%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20standing%20in%20a%20space%20that%20is%20both%20present%20and%20forward-looking%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20started%20to%20realize%20that%20letting%20go%20isn't%20something%20that%20happens%20the%20day%20your%20child%20leaves.%20It%20starts%20long%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229f5e2e18-33f2-4c47-9350-afed5fa90e79%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20role%20as%20his%20mother%20has%20changed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20already%20grieving%20a%20moment%20that%20hasn't%20happened%20yet.%20Every%20form%20we%20fill%20out%20feels%20like%20a%20step%20toward%20goodbye.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteaching-oldest-child-firstborn-to-set-boundaries-avoid-burnout-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoldest%20kid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20lately%20I%20find%20myself%20caught%20between%20who%20he%20is%20now%20and%20who%20he%20used%20to%20be.%20I%20think%20about%20his%20first%20steps%2C%20the%20early%20words%2C%20and%20the%20way%20he%20used%20to%20need%20me%20for%20everything.%20Back%20then%2C%20parenting%20felt%20physical.%20I%20was%20holding%2C%20guiding%2C%20and%20protecting%20him.%20Now%2C%20it%20feels%20internal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20past%20year%20has%20already%20been%20full%20of%20change.%20We%20moved%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleave-nyc-miami-retire-early-saving-unexpected-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20Portugal%2C%20a%20decision%20that%20reshaped%20our%20lives%20in%20ways%20I'm%20still%20processing.%20I%20left%20behind%20familiarity%2C%20stability%2C%20and%20everything%20we%20knew%20to%20build%20something%20new%20for%20us.%20That%20move%20required%20courage%2C%20trust%2C%20and%20letting%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20just%20as%20I've%20adjusted%20to%20this%20new%20life%2C%20I'm%20preparing%20to%20let%20go%20again%2C%20this%20time%20of%20my%20son%20as%20he%20steps%20into%20his%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257b95e6a-6787-4ac4-836c-5d6b233d7e1e%5C%22%3EI%20wonder%20if%20I've%20done%20everything%20I%20was%20supposed%20to%20do%20as%20his%20mom%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHave%20I%20prepared%20him%20enough%20for%20the%20world%3F%20For%20independence%3F%20For%20the%20moments%20when%20I%20won't%20be%20there%20to%20help%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20that's%20what%20scares%20me%20the%20most%3A%20not%20being%20by%20his%20side%20if%20something%20goes%20wrong%2C%20or%20not%20being%20able%20to%20step%20in%20quickly%2C%20fix%20it%2C%20and%20protect%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELetting%20go%20isn't%20a%20single%20moment%3B%20it's%20a%20process.%20It%20means%20encouraging%20him%20to%20make%20his%20own%20decisions%2C%20even%20when%20I%20want%20to%20guide%20them.%20It's%20teaching%20him%20how%20to%20manage%20his%20money%20and%20reminding%20him%20that%20he%20can't%20eat%20takeout%20every%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20watching%20him%20schedule%20his%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericas-healthcare-jobs-are-booming-hospitals-cant-meet-demand-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoctor%20appointments%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20handle%20his%20responsibilities%2C%20and%20figure%20things%20out%20on%20his%20own.%20I%20have%20to%20step%20back%20when%20my%20instinct%20is%20to%20step%20in.%20That's%20not%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20constant%20tension%20between%20wanting%20to%20protect%20him%20and%20knowing%20that%20growth%20requires%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dbf0bad7-c5cd-45e3-8cba-8749f494486e%5C%22%3EThis%20experience%20has%20created%20an%20internal%20shift%20in%20how%20I%20see%20parenting%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20so%20long%2C%20being%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-do-you-know-if-you-are-a-good-parent-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egood%20parent%3C%2Fa%3E%20meant%20being%20present%2C%20involved%2C%20and%20attentive%20to%20every%20need.%20Now%2C%20I'm%20realizing%20it%20also%20means%20knowing%20when%20to%20step%20back%20and%20not%20holding%20on%20too%20tightly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20to%20trust%20that%20what%20I've%20taught%20him%20will%20carry%20forward%2C%20even%20when%20I'm%20not%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20imagine%20the%20moments%20ahead%2C%20the%20ones%20we%20haven't%20reached%20yet%2C%20like%20him%20standing%20in%20a%20new%20apartment%20in%20a%20different%20country%2C%20calling%20me%20to%20ask%20how%20to%20fix%20a%20recipe.%20Or%20asking%20questions%20I%20used%20to%20answer%20before%20he%20even%20had%20to%20ask.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20I'll%20answer%20the%20same%20way%20every%20time%2C%20with%20patience%2C%20with%20love%2C%20and%20with%20delight.%20Because%20no%20matter%20how%20far%20he%20goes%2C%20I%20want%20him%20to%20know%20this%3A%20He%20can%20always%20call%20home%2C%20and%20I%20will%20always%20pick%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fson-studying-abroad-spain-mom-struggling-to-let-go-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774787821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c56c6548461c18d7be66bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fson-studying-abroad-spain-mom-struggling-to-let-go-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20son%20chose%20to%20study%20abroad%20in%20Spain%2C%20which%2