2%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22kids%20at%20summer%20camp%20running%20into%20a%20cabin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c572fe48461c18d7be6716%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223802%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20is%20struggling%20to%20find%20a%20summer%20camp%20for%20his%20kid.%3Cp%3EMaskot%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20summer%20camp%20for%20my%20child%2C%20since%20they'll%20be%20off%20for%2010%20weeks%20in%20a%20few%20months.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20are%20on%20multiple%20waiting%20lists%2C%20I%20lost%20money%2C%20and%20I'm%20still%20scrambling%20to%20find%20the%20best%20option.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20stress%20is%20even%20causing%20marital%20problems%2C%20as%20this%20is%20a%20childcare%20issue%20most%20Americans%20face.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kindergartner%20is%20currently%20signed%20up%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwent-to-sleepaway-camp-older-women-confidence-aging-lessons-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esummer%20camp%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20a%20location%2C%20a%20backup%20one%20without%20a%20starting%20date%2C%20and%20three%20waitlist%20lotteries.%20One%20organizer%20described%20our%20odds%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20fat%20chance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20only%20March.%20Summer%20is%20still%20several%20months%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20country%2C%20parents%20like%20me%20are%20in%20our%20annual%20scramble%20to%20piece%20together%20summer%20plans%20that%20balance%20affordability%2C%20availability%2C%20and%2C%20if%20we're%20lucky%2C%20advancement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b191ec06-ed3f-4ed3-98fd-29b56beb80f1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EScheduling%20out%2010%20weeks%20for%20my%20children%20in%20the%20summer%20is%20difficult%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20and%20I%20are%20raising%20two%20young%20kids%20in%20Philadelphia%2C%20relying%20largely%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbasic-income-gbi-ubi-low-income-americans-afford-housing-food-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecity-supported%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20are%20reasonably%20well-run%20and%20relatively%20accessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParents%20across%20the%20country%20face%20a%20familiar%20puzzle%3A%20navigating%20a%20fractured%20landscape%20of%20camps%2C%20lotteries%2C%20and%20deposits%20to%20keep%20kids%20safe%20and%20enriched.%20Programs%20with%20excess%20availability%20often%20lack%20resources.%20Programs%20in%20high%20demand%20often%20lack%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%20week%20this%20summer%2C%20our%20preferred%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-affordable-places-to-live-in-america-lowest-cost-living-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow-cost%20neighborhood%3C%2Fa%3E%20arts%20camp%20had%20a%20lottery%20whose%20deadline%20had%20not%20yet%20closed.%20A%20similar%20program%20farther%20away%20required%20payment%20sooner.%20Not%20wanting%20to%20miss%20out%2C%20we%20applied%20for%20both.%20We%20got%20into%20the%20farther-away%20camp%20first%2C%20which%20required%20an%20immediate%20nonrefundable%20deposit%20%E2%80%94%20about%20%24300.%20A%20few%20days%20later%2C%20we%20learned%20we'd%20gotten%20into%20our%20preferred%20neighborhood%20camp%20after%20all.%20The%20result%3A%20we%20simply%20lost%20the%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20one%20week%20out%20of%20the%20roughly%2010%20weeks%20of%20summer%20we%20have%20to%20cover%20between%20the%20end%20of%20school%20and%20the%20start%20of%20the%20next%20year.%20As%20kids%20age%2C%20pressure%20mounts%20to%20stuff%20the%20summer%20with%20extra-curriculars%2C%20though%20there's%20value%20in%20giving%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsweden-to-los-angeles-american-playdates-culture-shock-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunstructured%20independence%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20young%20kids%20need%20to%20be%20minded%20while%20mom%20and%20dad%20are%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2268b93a52-7c2e-44ec-9f3f-b765c6106744%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20annual%20scramble%20has%20a%20structural%20cause%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20schools%20typically%20close%2010%20to%2012%20weeks%20each%20summer%2C%20a%20calendar%20that%20dates%20to%20agricultural%20schedules%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsole-breadwinner-single-income-family-budget-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esingle-income%20households%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20today%2C%20more%20American%20couples%20are%20dual%20earners%2C%20meaning%20both%20are%20working%20during%20the%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFew%20summer%20programs%20cover%20the%20full%20break.%20Parents%20must%20build%20their%20own%20patchwork%20system%20to%20bridge%20that%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20costs%20add%20up%20quickly.%20The%20average%20camp%20costs%20%2480%20per%20day%2C%20and%20twice%20that%20for%20overnight%20camps%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbipartisanpolicy.org%2Farticle%2Fstate-child-care-data-2025-update%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Camp%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%20prices%20range%20widely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultiply%20%24400%20or%20more%20a%20week%20by%20several%20weeks%20per%20child%2C%20and%20the%20numbers%20climb%20fast.%20Even%20relying%20on%20city-run%20programs%2C%20we'll%20spend%20several%20thousand%20dollars%20programming%20our%20kindergartner%20this%20summer%2C%20and%20that's%20on%20top%20of%20our%20youngest%2C%20who%20is%20still%20in%20daycare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scramble%20hurts%20both%20kids%2C%20their%20parents%2C%20and%20the%20wider%20economy.%20Last%20fall%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbipartisanpolicy.org%2Farticle%2Feconomic-impact-of-americas-child-care-gap%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBipartisan%20Policy%20Center%3C%2Fa%3E%20estimated%20a%20looming%20%24329%20billion%20loss%20over%20the%20next%2010%20years%20due%20to%20workforce%20shortages%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20childcare%20gap%20that%20deepens%20when%20schools%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20wealthy%20countries%2C%20the%20problem%20is%20often%20less%20acute.%20Many%20have%20shorter%20summer%20breaks%20or%20integrate%20childcare%20more%20directly%20with%20school%20systems.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20the%20burden%20falls%20largely%20on%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20every%20year%2C%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20year%2C%20families%20start%20playing%20a%20strange%20logistical%20game%3A%20mapping%20out%20calendars%2C%20tracking%20lottery%20deadlines%2C%20comparing%20deposits%2C%20and%20trying%20to%20avoid%20the%20weeks%20that%20might%20otherwise%20collapse%20into%20childcare%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22446f9ebe-0b3d-4dbe-a610-885ea778023e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20our%20house%2C%20that%20process%20is%20still%20underway%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20missing%20out%20on%20multiple%20lotteries%20for%20the%20most%20in-demand%2C%20nearby%20programs%2C%20I%20paid%20a%20registration%20fee%20for%20a%20different%20day%20camp%20while%20we%20wait%20to%20find%20out%20where%20that%20camp%20will%20be%20physically%20located.%20Another%20week%20is%20covered%20by%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-vacation-travel-more-budget-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamily%20vacation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20we've%20decided%20to%20shift%20a%20long%20weekend%20with%20friends%20into%20weekdays%20%E2%80%94%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20will%20be%20using%20scarce%20time%20off%20from%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20we're%20lucky.%20The%20city%20programs%20are%20relatively%20affordable%2C%20neighbors%20exchange%20tips%2C%20and%20we%20can%20cover%20the%20other%20costs.%20The%20real%20toll%20is%20logistical%20stress%20%E2%80%94%20the%20spreadsheets%2C%20the%20lottery%20calendars%2C%20the%20backup%20plans%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20occasional%20marital%20bickering%20that%20comes%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20and%20I%20recently%20exchanged%20icy%20updates%20as%20we%20evaluated%20our%20five-year-old's%20summertime%20calendar%20as%20if%20we%20were%20planning%20an%20already-delayed%20product%20launch.%20Some%20costs%20of%20the%20summertime%20schedule%20scramble%20are%20clearer%20than%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdad-scrambling-summer-camp-plans-lost-money-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774784221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c57467732a0245147138ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdad-scrambling-summer-camp-plans-lost-money-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20kids%20are%20off%20for%2010%20weeks%20this%20summer.%20I'm%20struggling%20to%20find%20a%20summer%20camp%20that%20will%20fill%20that%20time.%20Some%20camps%20are%20full%20or%20too%20expensive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Christopher%20Wink)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdad-scrambling-summer-camp-plans-lost-money-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Clavicular%20storms%20out%20of%20Andrew%20Callaghan%20interview%20after%20tense%20exchange%20over%20%E2%80%9Clooksmaxxing%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774784160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129876351%2Cimgsize-26410.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus-streamers%2Fclavicular-storms-out-of-andrew-callaghan-interview-after-tense-exchange-over-looksmaxxing%2Farticleshow%2F129876351.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20