%20kids%20have%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20dropped%20my%20cover-up.%20A%20pit%20formed%20in%20my%20stomach%20as%20it%20does%20each%20year%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-for-splitting-the-holidays-divorced-family-partner-2017-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eholidays%20coincide%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20we%20host.%20It's%20so%20much%20work%2C%20and%20neither%20holiday%20ends%20up%20feeling%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20kids%20were%20younger%2C%20demands%20came%20from%20the%20grandparents%20who%20wanted%20the%20children%20to%20be%20fully%20immersed%20in%20their%20cultures%20and%20religious%20traditions.%20My%20mother%20wooed%20them%20with%20elaborate%20goody-stuffed%20Easter%20baskets%2C%20while%20their%20other%20grandma%20showered%20them%20with%20Passover%20plague%20finger%20puppets%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-do-coke-bottles-have-yellow-caps-2017-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eseder%20coloring%20books%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20shuttled%20them%20from%20New%20Jersey%20to%20Long%20Island%2C%20to%20New%20Jersey%2C%20to%20Staten%20Island%2C%20and%20back%20to%20New%20Jersey%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20my%20children%20grow%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-50s-combat-brain-fog-stay-sharp-prevent-cognitive-decline-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eadditional%20stress%3C%2Fa%3E%20stems%20from%20getting%20my%20oldest%20home%20from%20college%2C%20fitting%20celebrations%20in%20with%20school%20schedules%2C%20and%20knowing%20that%20as%20we%20reach%20new%20milestones%2C%20things%20will%20continue%20to%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20with%20the%20bitter-sweet%20reminder%20that%20my%20middle%20child%20is%20poised%20to%20fly%20the%20nest%20hovering%20in%20my%20mind%2C%20I'll%20channel%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-from-new-york-to-los-angeles-differences-between-coasts-2020-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elaid-back%20West%20Coast%20vibe%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20take%20a%20deep%20breath%2C%20and%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20make%20it%20all%20work%20%E2%80%94%20without%20losing%20sight%20of%20what's%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22721d5deb-4dd9-4c0a-8459-3dc1ced1f314%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPassover%20and%20Easter%20are%20so%20opposite%20that%20sometimes%20it's%20comical%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20part%20of%20a%20religiously%20mixed%20family%2C%20onlookers%20can't%20see%20the%20differences%2C%20but%20you%20can%20certainly%20feel%20them.%20I%20mean%2C%20what%20do%20Easter%20and%20Passover%20have%20in%20common%20besides%20eggs%3F%20Not%20much.%20There%20is%20the%20ritual%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-easter-fun-facts-stats-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehiding%20Easter%20eggs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20hiding%20the%20afikomen%20(matzoh)%20for%20the%20kids%20to%20hunt.%20But%2C%20I%20swear%20that's%20the%20only%20commonality%20I've%20found%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Easter%20baskets%20piled%20high%20sit%20atop%20a%20dining%20room%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c57edf48461c18d7be67b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222448%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20said%20she%20does%20her%20best%20to%20honor%20traditions%20from%20her%20husband's%20Jewish%20faith%20and%20her%20Italian-Catholic%20upbringing.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Holly%20Rizzuto%20Palker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFluffy%20bunnies%20and%20frogs%20(one%20of%20the%20ten%20plagues%20represented%20during%20the%20seder)%20aren't%20even%20the%20same%20species.%20But%20since%20they're%20happy%20little%20spring%20critters%20that%20take%20center%20stage%20during%20Easter%20and%20Passover%2C%20when%20my%20kids%20were%20youngsters%2C%20we%20leaned%20heavily%20into%20filling%20the%20week%20with%20chocolate%20rabbits%20and%20googly-eyed%20stuffed%20frogs%20because%20they're%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatzoh%20balls%20versus%20meatballs%3A%20now%20those%20are%20difficult%20spheres%20to%20reconcile.%20I%20mean%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-stopped-believing-in-santa-new-holiday-christmas-tradition-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emy%20Italian%20family%3C%2Fa%3E%20gorges%20on%20carbs%20during%20Easter%20weekend%2C%20and%20the%20Jewish%20side%20abstains%20from%20grain%20for%20the%20whole%20week.%20To%20bridge%20the%20two%2C%20I've%20devised%20a%20meal%20called%20%26quot%3BErev%20Passover%20Marinara%2C%26quot%3B%20during%20which%20I%20serve%20meatballs%20the%20night%20before%20the%20Passover%20seder%20begins.%20It%20satisfies%20a%20few%20traditions%20at%20once%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2281824e3c-4832-4af3-bcf5-8f2619ca7370%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20bend%20the%20rules%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20as%20we%20roast%20an%20egg%20in%20the%20oven%2C%20to%20represent%20the%20circle%20of%20life%20on%20our%20symbolic%20seder%20plate%2C%20we'll%20color%20Easter%20eggs%2C%20too.%20My%20husband%20will%20make%20time%20for%20it%2C%20even%20if%20that%20means%20abridging%20the%20Haggadah%20during%20the%20first%20night%20of%20seder.%20Why%3F%20He%20understands%20that%20since%20we've%20decided%20to%20raise%20our%20children%20in%20his%20Jewish%20faith%2C%20I%20hold%20Catholic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fupdating-holiday-traditions-for-a-growing-blended-family-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eholiday%20traditions%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20more%20dear%20as%20a%20link%20to%20my%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatzoh%20brei%2C%20the%20morning-after-seder%20sugar-covered%2C%20breadless%20version%20of%20French%20toast%2C%20is%20a%20no-brainer.%20Does%20it%20mean%2C%20however%2C%20we%20won't%20eat%20semolina%20on%20Easter%20Sunday%20even%20if%20it%20falls%20during%20the%20week%20of%20Passover%3F%20No.%20A%20number%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20my%20husband%20conceded%20that%20it%20wasn't%20practical%20to%20keep%20things%20grain-free%20for%20the%20entire%20week%20of%20Passover%20when%20Easter%20overlapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20me%2C%20although%20attending%20Catholic%20School%20embedded%20strict%20rules%20in%20my%20mind%2C%20the%20edicts%20can%20be%20impossible%20to%20follow%20during%20Passover.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20Good%20Friday%20falls%20during%20a%20seder%20meal%2C%20I'll%20repent%20and%20eat%20meat%2C%20refusing%20to%20believe%20I'll%20be%20punished.%20And%20so%20we%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22300e9d02-b008-4018-b784-77ad05e8c8b9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe've%20gained%20perspective%20on%20how%20to%20make%20it%20work%20for%20our%20family%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20many%20years%20for%20us%20to%20tune%20out%20the%20extended%20family%20noise%20and%20focus%20on%20our%20kids'%20holiday%20celebrations.%20Knowing%20the%20grandparents%20meant%20well%2C%20but%20rising%20above%20the%20underlying%20push-and-pull%20when%20Easter%20and%20Passover%20coincided%20wasn't%20easy.%20Bunnies%2C%20church%2C%20matzoh%2C%20seder%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20dizzying.%20We%20learned%20to%20improvise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20as%20I%20lay%20plague%20finger%20puppet%20on%20each%20Passover%20plate%2C%20I'll%20try%20to%20concentrate%20on%20being%20lucky%20enough%20to%20have%20all%20three%20of%20my%20kids%20and%20three%20of%20the%20grandparents%20(unfortunately%2C%20my%20mother-in-law%20has%20passed)%20with%20us%20to%20celebrate%20both%20magical%20holidays.%20Who%20knows%20where%20my%20son%20will%20go%20to%20college%20once%20he%20graduates%3F%20I%20hope%20he'll%20be%20able%20to%20join%20us.%20After%20all%2C%20being%20together%20as%20a%20family%20is%20what%20matters%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feaster-passover-overlap-family-celebrations-tricky-honor-both-faiths-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774780381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c57e3148461c18d7be67b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feaster-passover-overlap-family-celebrations-tricky-honor-both-faiths-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20past%2C%20when%20Easter%20and%20Passover%20overlapped%2C%20my%20stress%20levels%20were%20high.%20Now%20I%20know%20I%20need%20to%20bend%20some%20rules%20to%20honor%20both%20holidays.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Holly%20Rizzuto%20Palker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feaster-passover-overlap-family-celebrations-tricky-honor-both-faiths-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Can't%20do%20a%20pull-up%3F%20This%20Marine%20colonel%20told%20us%20how%20to%20get%20your%20first%20rep%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Marine%20corps%20colonel%20Misty%20Posey's%20pull-up%20program%20has%20become%20a%20popular%20method%20for%20some%20Marines%20hoping%20to%20boost%20their%20reps.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bda7215b58f1f0f9335be1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarine%20Corps%20colonel%20Misty%20Posey's%20pull-up%20program%20has%20become%20a%20popular%20method%20for%20some%20Marines%20hoping%20to%20boost%20their%20reps.%20Here%2C%20Posey%2C%20far%20left%2C%20coaches%20some%20students.%3Cp%3ELance%20Cpl.%20Cody%20Fitzgerald%2FUS%20Marine%20Corps%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20struggling%20to%20get%20her%20first%20pull-up%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20a%20Marine%20built%20a%20pull-up%20program%20used%20across%20the%20Corps%20today.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20colonel%20says%20most%20people%20can%20get%20their%20first%20reps%20faster%20than%20they%20think.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHer%20method%20leans%20on%20partner-assisted%20pull-ups%20and%20avoiding%20burnout.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20petite%204%20feet%2C%2010%20inches%2C%20Misty%20Posey%20couldn't%20rely%20on%20her%20height%20to%20clear%20the%20Marine%20Corps%20obstacle%20course%20as%20a%20prospective%20young%20recruit.%20Instead%2C%20she%20learned%20to%20pull%20her%20entire%20body%20over%20it%2C%20eventually%20developing%20a%20pull-up%20program%20now%20used%20across%20the%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPosey%2C%20who%20is%20now%2049%20and%20a%20commanding%20officer%20leading%20a%20Marine%20unit%20in%20California%2C%20didn't%20grow%20up%20lifting%20weights%20and%20avoided%20strength%20training%20until%20she%20was%20in%20her%2030s%20for%20fear%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbulking-gain-muscle-faster-winter-season-expert-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebulking%20up%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20a%20worry%2C%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20that%20was%20misplaced%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPull-ups%20are%20a%20key%20strength%20training%20tool%20that%20builds%20full%20upper-body%20strength%2C%20grip%2C%20and%20core%20stability%20while%20improving%20posture%20and%20functional%20fitness.%20They're%20a%20highly%20efficient%2C%20scalable%20exercise%20that%20also%20supports%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-the-marine-corps-top-enlisted-leader-stays-in-shape-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejoint%20health%20and%20bone%20density%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20important%20for%20longevity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20many%2C%20the%20thought%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpull-ups-how-to-improve-do-your-first-one-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edoing%20a%20pull-up%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20daunting%20and%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20seemingly%20impossible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20actually%20as%20hard%20as%20many%20people%20might%20think%20to%20learn%20to%20do%20a%20pull-up%2C%20said%20Posey%2C%20who%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emaxes%20around%2020%20reps.%20%26quot%3BYou've%20got%20to%20do%20the%20work.%20But%20there's%20some%20tricks%20of%20the%20trade%20in%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20own%20pull-up%20journey%20began%20in%20her%20Reserve%20Officer%20Training%20Corps%20group%20as%20an%20undergrad%20at%20the%20University%20of%20San%20Diego%20back%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20after%20she%20decided%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20the%20Marines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20small%20stature%20meant%20she%20lacked%20the%20height%20needed%20to%20more%20easily%20clear%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-marines-train-on-a-confidence-course-in-boot-camp-2020-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eobstacle%20course%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20rigorous%20physical%20test%20with%20stacked%20pull-up%20bars%2C%20a%20leap%20to%20raised%20parallel%20logs%2C%20and%20a%20tall%20wall%20to%20climb%20over%2C%20among%20other%20challenges.%20So%20she%20had%20to%20learn%20to%20pull%20her%20body%20over%20walls%20and%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20tried%20machines%20and%20band-assisted%20work%20and%20made%20slow%20progress%20before%20a%20Marine%20mentor%20finally%20pushed%20her%20onto%20a%20real%20pull-up%20bar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20my%20first%20chin-up%20in%20three%20days%20after%20I%20was%20given%20proper%20training%20advice%2C%26quot%3B%20Posey%20said%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Erecalling%20the%20mix%20of%20excitement%20and%20disbelief%20when%20she%20first%20pulled%20herself%20all%20the%20way%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228003%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Colonel%20Misty%20Posey%20leads%20a%20pull-up%20workshop%20at%20Twentynine%20Palms%2C%20California%2C%20Feb.%2017%2C%202026.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6b8b6445048b5f68bbb72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225338%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPartner-assistance%2C%20partial%20pull-ups%2C%20jumping%20pull-ups%2C%20and%20negatives%20are%20four%20key%20ways%20to%20master%20the%20movement%2C%20according%20to%20Posey's%20program.%3Cp%3ELance%20Cpl.%20Cody%20Fitzgerald%2FUS%20Marine%20Corps%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20she%20did%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20when%20it%20clicked%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPosey%2C%20now%20a%20colonel%2C%20first%20started%20to%20gain%20attention%20over%20a%20decade%20ago%20after%20another%20Marine%20happened%20to%20mention%20her%20informal%20program%20efforts%20to%20the%20Corps'%20top%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20the%20service%20was%20undergoing%20a%20shift%20in%20its%20physical%20fitness%20standards.%20While%20men%20tested%20their%20upper-body%20strength%20with%20pull-ups%2C%20women%20had%20long%20performed%20a%20flexed-arm%20hang.%20But%20in%202014%2C%20that%20changed%20%E2%80%94%20women%20were%20newly%20mandated%20to%20also%20do%20pull-ups%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20so%20many%20Marines%20suddenly%20focused%20on%20pull-ups%2C%20the%20general%20reached%20out%20to%20Posey%20to%20promote%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eher%20program%20more%20broadly%2C%20she%20said.%20That%20gave%20it%20a%20major%20boost%20within%20the%20Corps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto%3Ffbid%3D1358941689602302%26set%3Dpcb.1358963312933473%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20Posey%20said%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20others%2C%20is%20used%20by%20potential%20recruits%20who%20have%20never%20done%20a%20single%20pull-up%20and%20seasoned%20Marines%20wanting%20to%20get%20their%20numbers%20up.%20She%20also%20leads%20small%20training%20sessions%20for%20anyone%2C%20service%20members%20or%20civilians%2C%20on%20base%20looking%20to%20take%20their%20reps%20to%20the%20next%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnybody%20in%20reasonable%20shape%20can%20learn%20to%20lift%20their%20own%20body%20weight%2C%26quot%3B%20Posey%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20could%20do%20it%2C%20anybody%20can.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228d93eff1-b978-48a5-8921-f80f2cba3084%5C%22%3EHow%20she%20teaches%20Marines%20to%20do%20pull-ups%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20sure%20where%20to%20begin%3F%20Posey%20recommends%20testing%20your%20current%20strength%20first%3A%20from%20a%20dead%20hang%20on%20a%20pull-up%20bar%20with%20your%20palms%20facing%20away%2C%20pull%20yourself%20up%20as%20far%20as%20you%20can.%20Work%20within%20whatever%20range%20of%20motion%20you%20have%2C%20then%20drop%20down%2C%20rest%2C%20and%20repeat%20%E2%80%94%20focusing%20on%20engaging%20your%20core%20and%20back%20before%20each%20rep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20can't%20do%20a%20pull-up%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fchin-up-vs-pull-up%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etry%20a%20chin-up%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20your%20palms%20facing%20your%20body%20instead%20of%20away.%20This%20approach%20can%20be%20easier%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMake%20sure%20to%20rest%20between%20attempts%2C%20anywhere%20from%20two%20to%20five%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225616%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Posey%20has%20led%20pull-up%20workshops%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20including%20this%20training%20at%20Quantico%2C%20Virginia%2C%20Feb.%2019%2C%202016.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6bc2c8e44c01630d31863%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223159%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPosey%20has%20led%20pull-up%20workshops%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20including%20this%20training%20at%20Quantico%2C%20Virginia%2C%20Feb.%2019%2C%202016.%3Cp%3ESgt.%20Dylan%20Bowyer%2FUS%20Marine%20Corps%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20option%20for%20people%20just%20starting%20out%20is%20to%20enlist%20a%20friend%20to%20help.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20a%20partner%20wanting%20your%20first%20pull-up%2C%20that's%20absolutely%20helpful%2C%26quot%3B%20Posey%20said.%20%26quot%3BPartner%20pull-ups%20are%20the%20number%20one%20way%20to%20get%20your%20first%20pull-up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20partner%20can%20help%20finish%20reps%20by%20gently%20supporting%20your%20lower%20back%20area%2C%20providing%20a%20little%20help%20on%20the%20ascent%20and%20control%20on%20a%20slowed%20descent%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsetting-physical-goals-helped-me-get-older-essay-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuild%20strength%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20slow%20descents%20are%20called%20%26quot%3Bnegatives%26quot%3B%20and%20are%20another%20great%20method%20for%20boosting%20reps%2C%20Posey%20said%2C%20though%20she%20cautioned%20against%20doing%20them%20excessively%2C%20since%20they%20can%20take%20a%20toll%20on%20the%20body%2C%20straining%20or%20damaging%20muscles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20thing%20to%20avoid%2C%20she%20said%2C%20is%20overreliance%20on%20bands%20or%20assist%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20tension%20on%20the%20band%20is%20in%20the%20bottom%20position%20of%20the%20pull-up%2C%20which%20is%20where%20the%20pull-up%20is%20initiated%2C%26quot%3B%20Posey%20said%2C%20explaining%20that%20too%20many%20aids%20can%20make%20it%20harder%20to%20build%20strength.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20hardest%20part%20of%20the%20pull-up%20for%20most%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20any%20pull-up%2C%20proper%20technique%20is%20critical%2C%20she%20said%2C%20and%20so%20is%20the%20bar%20height.%20If%20the%20bar%20is%20too%20high%20to%20reach%20comfortably%2C%20use%20a%20sturdy%20box%20to%20step%20up.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuild-more-muscle-less-time-pro-tips-top-exercise-scientist-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EProper%20setup%20and%20technique%3C%2Fa%3E%20matter%20as%20much%20as%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlternating%20partial%20reps%20with%20jumping%20reps%2C%20where%20you%20use%20a%20small%20jump%20to%20reach%20the%20top%20and%20then%20lower%20yourself%20under%20control%2C%20to%20practice%20the%20full%20movement%2C%20helps%20to%20build%20strength%2C%20Posey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20any%20kind%20of%20repetition%2C%20including%20range%20of%20motion%2C%20jumping%20pull-ups%2C%20or%20negatives%2C%20the%20key%20is%20knowing%20when%20to%20stop.%20It's%20not%20something%20you%20do%20to%20failure%2C%20she%20said%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecautioning%20against%20maxing%20out%20sets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStriking%20the%20right%20balance%20between%20challenging%20your%20body%20but%20not%20overdoing%20it%20is%20essential%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20many%20Marines%20who%20reach%20out%20to%20Posey%2C%20many%20are%20either%20not%20doing%20enough%20pull-ups%20%E2%80%94%20relying%20too%20much%20on%20supplemental%20exercises%20like%20push-ups%20or%20bench%20press%2C%20or%20not%20training%20pull-ups%20frequently%20enough%20%E2%80%94%20or%20they're%20overdoing%20it%2C%20which%20can%20burn%20out%20the%20central%20nervous%20system%20and%20lead%20to%20injuries%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20doing%20small%20sub-max%2C%20a%20person%20can%20typically%20accumulate%20more%20repetitions%2C%20more%20volume%2C%20and%20that's%20where%20you%20succeed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarine-colonel-how-to-get-your-first-pull-up-rep-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774780321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c67c8346a3e043bdfc5bbe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarine-colonel-how-to-get-your-first-pull-up-rep-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Marine%20colonel%20behind%20the%20Corps'%20pull-up%20training%20shares%20simple%20tips%20to%20he