img%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joe%20Fenti%3B%20Kelly%20He-Sun%3B%20Jack%20Kim%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c71d0f8373a547629c7488%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20young%20consultants%20are%20leaving%20the%20industry%20are%20turning%20towards%20content%20creation%20instead%20of%20the%20traditional%20exit%20opportunities.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Joe%20Fenti%3B%20Courtesy%20of%20Kelly%20He-Sun%3B%20Courtesy%20of%20Jack%20Kim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThere's%20a%20surprising%20new%20exit%20opportunity%20for%20elite%20consultants%3A%20social%20media%20and%20content%20creation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThree%20former%20consultants%20said%20they%20successfully%20leveraged%20their%20consulting%20experience%20for%20content.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECorporate%20influencers%20are%20on%20the%20rise%2C%20from%20LinkedIn%20to%20TikTok.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EKelly%20He-Sun%20landed%20one%20of%20the%20corporate%20world's%20most%20competitive%20jobs%20as%20a%20consultant%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbcg-head-of-people-ai-core-competencies-performance-evaluations-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoston%20Consulting%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20got%20promoted%20to%20a%20project%20leader%20by%20age%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20didn't%20see%20herself%20doing%20consulting%20forever%2C%20so%20in%202024%2C%20she%20quit%20after%20almost%20six%20years.%20She%20planned%20to%20spend%20time%20traveling%20and%20creating%20fashion%20and%20lifestyle%20content%2C%20but%20when%20she%20made%20a%20video%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-4-consulting-big-tech-ey-meta-compared-career-pivot-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20in%20consulting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20took%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20made%20a%20video%20about%20the%20number%20of%20hours%20we%20typically%20work%2C%20and%20it%20just%20blew%20up.%20I%20didn't%20expect%20it%20to%20draw%20that%20kind%20of%20attention%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20when%20I%20started%20realizing%2C%20'Wow%2C%20people%20are%20really%20interested%20in%20this%20type%20of%20content.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe-Sun%20is%20among%20a%20growing%20group%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsulting-has-a-gen-z-problem-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGen%20Z%20and%20millennial%20consultants%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewho%20are%20trading%20traditional%20exit%20opportunities%20for%20content%20creation.%20Posts%20about%20consulting%20rack%20up%20thousands%20of%20views%20on%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram%2C%20while%20the%20%23corporatelife%20hashtag%20has%20over%201.7%20million%20posts%20on%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20consultants%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmbb-explained-mckinsey-bain-bcg-compare-big-three-strategy-consultants-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etop%20firms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20MBB%20or%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-four-earnings-compared-ey-deloitte-pwc-kpmg-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Four%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20includes%20McKinsey%2C%20Bain%2C%20and%20BCG%2C%20and%20PwC%2C%20KPMG%2C%20Deloitte%2C%20and%20EY%20%E2%80%94%20their%20background%20can%20signal%20credibility%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20chance%20to%20get%20an%20insider's%20perspective%20into%20an%20industry%20that's%20famous%20for%20its%20secrecy%20and%20notoriously%20competitive%20to%20break%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20consultants-turned-content%20creators%20told%20Business%20Insider%20how%20they%20leveraged%20their%20high-profile%20jobs%20into%20lucrative%20exits%20with%20the%20help%20of%20social%20media%2C%20and%20why%20they%20have%20no%20plans%20to%20go%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226fc0e174-90eb-46c3-a970-4ac6465b61c4%5C%22%3EContent%20creation%20can%20be%20as%20lucrative%20as%20consulting%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHe-Sun%20posts%20all%20about%20consulting%20and%20general%20career%20tips%2C%20like%20about%20how%20she%20became%20one%20of%20the%20youngest%20managers%20at%20a%20top%20consulting%20firm%20and%20how%20to%20ask%20for%20help%20while%20still%20sounding%20competent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20started%20posting%20in%202024%2C%20she%20ramped%20up%20her%20strategy%20in%202025.%20So%20far%20in%202026%2C%20she's%20made%20around%20%2442%2C000.%20With%20over%2050%2C000%20followers%20between%20Instagram%20and%20TikTok%2C%20He-Sun%20makes%20most%20of%20her%20money%20through%20brand%20deals%2C%20but%20has%20also%20earned%20through%20affiliate%20marketing%2C%20user-generated%20content%2C%20and%201%3A1%20coaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20Fenti%2C%20who%20has%20over%20800%2C000%20followers%20across%20accounts%2C%20left%20his%20job%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-big-four-consultant-quit-content-creator-corporate-culture-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Four%20consulting%20firm%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202024%20to%20become%20a%20full-time%20comedian%20and%20content%20creator.%20Fenti%20also%20capitalizes%20on%20his%20background%20by%20roasting%20consulting%20and%20corporate%20culture.%20One%20sketch%2C%20titled%20%26quot%3BTimesheets%20In%20Consulting%20Make%20No%20Sense%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20racked%20up%20more%20than%202.2%20million%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2029-year-old%20started%20posting%20content%20while%20he%20was%20still%20working%20at%20his%20firm%2C%20but%20finally%20quit%20when%20the%20money%20he%20was%20making%20from%20content%2C%20primarily%20via%20brand%20deals%2C%20exceeded%20his%20consulting%20salary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJack%20Kim%2C%20a%2029-year-old%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-mbb-consultant-says-getting-job-offer-is-about-the-airplane-test-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equit%20his%20job%20at%20Bain%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%2C%20started%20posting%20about%20consulting%20on%20YouTube%20while%20he%20was%20still%20at%20the%20firm%20and%20realized%20there%20was%20a%20huge%20audience%20looking%20for%20insights%20on%20breaking%20into%20consulting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20his%20friend%20now%20run%20Casebuddy%2C%20a%20one-on-one%20mentorship%20business%20that%20helps%20take%20clients%20through%20the%20entire%20process%20of%20landing%20a%20consulting%20job%2C%20from%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20writing%20to%20acing%20case%20interviews.%20They%20charge%20between%20around%20%241%2C300%20and%20%246%2C700%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20service%2C%20and%20he%20said%20most%20people%20applying%20for%20the%20program%20find%20it%20through%20his%20social%20media%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d73acf70-be39-48cc-b1dc-8b02345fd97c%5C%22%3EA%20growing%20opportunity%20in%20the%20creator%20economy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20mostly%20associated%20with%20consumer%20brands%2C%20influencer%20marketing%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20important%20to%20B2B%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20and%20those%20companies%20often%20want%20to%20work%20with%20creators%20whose%20audience%20includes%20working%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhereas%20lifestyle%20influencers%20might%20get%20brand%20deals%20with%20retailers%20like%20Walmart%20or%20Sephora%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-expanding-video-feed-how-creators-grow-audience-tiktok-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecorporate%20influencers%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20score%20brand%20deals%20with%20SaaS%20companies.%20Fenti%20has%20worked%20with%20Grammarly%20and%20Scribe%2C%20while%20He-Sun%20has%20partnered%20with%20Microsoft%2C%20Indeed%2C%20and%20several%20SaaS%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20in%20this%20era%20of%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20B2B%20creator%2C%26quot%3B%20Brendan%20Gahan%2C%20founder%20of%20Creator%20Authority%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20number%20of%20creators%20focused%20on%20business%20and%20corporate%20life%20was%20%26quot%3Bexploding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20growth%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-courts-creators-with-new-slate-of-video-shows-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20content%20creators%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20way%20executives%20at%20major%20companies%20have%20become%20de%20facto%20influencers.%20McKinsey%20has%20promoted%20its%20own%20%26quot%3Btop%20voices%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20list%20that%20included%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-workforce-ai-agents-consulting-industry-bob-sternfels-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBob%20Sternfels%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Lara%20Sophie%20Bothur%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20how%20she%20became%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeloitte-corporate-influencer-lara-sophie-bothur-linkedin-value-of-employees-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeloitte%20Germany's%20first%20corporate%20influencer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGahan%20said%20B2B%20influencer%20marketing%20was%20expected%20to%20be%20worth%20%247.7%20billion%20by%20the%20end%20of%202025.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbusiness.linkedin.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fbusiness%2Fmarketing-solutions%2Fglobal%2Fen_US%2Fsite%2Fpdf%2Fwp%2F2025%2F2025-b2b-marketing-benchmark-trust-is-the-new-kpi.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%202025%20found%20that%20B2B%20marketers%20use%20influencers%20to%20raise%20brand%20awareness%2C%20build%20trust%2C%20and%20convert%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGahan%20said%20influencers%20can%20help%20shape%20the%20reputation%20and%20opinion%20of%20a%20brand%2C%20and%20in%20turn%20influence%20the%20decision%20makers%20inside%20companies.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20a%20bunch%20of%20consultants%20at%20a%20firm%20become%20interested%20in%20a%20software%20product%20they've%20seen%20promoted%20online%2C%20it's%20more%20likely%20their%20company%20will%20be%20interested%20in%20buying%20that%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226537e339-11be-43dc-a38d-2a125cd5c911%5C%22%3EA%20glimpse%20into%20the%20mystery%20of%20consulting%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EConsulting%20is%20a%20notoriously%20secretive%2C%20prestigious%2C%20and%20high-paying%20industry%2C%20so%20naturally%2C%20plenty%20of%20young%20professionals%20are%20hungry%20for%20the%20inside%20scoop%20on%20how%20it%20works%20and%20how%20to%20break%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKim%20said%20when%20he%20was%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-is-changing-consulting-talent-at-mckinsey-pwc-deloitte-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapplying%20to%20consulting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20found%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20more%20information%20online%20about%20how%20to%20break%20into%20fields%20like%20finance%20and%20law%2C%20while%20consulting%20was%20still%20a%20mystery.%20%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20really%20able%20to%20find%20anyone%20that%20was%20specifically%20doing%20consultant%20content%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFenti%20said%20he%20thinks%20the%20content%20resonates%20because%20consulting%20can%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bnebulous%26quot%3B%20industry%20full%20of%20%26quot%3Bfluff%20answers%26quot%3B%20about%20what%20consultants%20actually%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20thinks%20his%20jokes%20about%20consulting%20and%20corporate%20culture%20resonate%20because%20the%20MBB%20and%20Big%20Four%20firms%20collectively%20employ%20over%20a%20million%20people%2C%20and%20it's%20%26quot%3Bnice%20to%20see%20the%20world%20you%20live%20reflected%20back%20to%20you%20and%20to%20see%20the%20frustrations%20you%20feel%20is%20also%20felt%20elsewhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20creators%20currently%20has%20plans%20to%20return%20to%20the%20corporate%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20grind%20of%20consulting%2C%20He-Sun%20said%20she%20finds%20content%20creation%20work%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Breally%20easy%26quot%3B%20in%20comparison%2C%20and%20she%20plans%20to%20expand%20her%20revenue%20streams%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKim%20said%20that%20he%20loves%20his%20mentorship%20business%20and%20has%20plans%20to%20continue%20growing%20it%2C%20but%20ultimately%20wants%20to%20become%20a%20much%20bigger%20content%20creator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFenti%20wants%20to%20do%20more%20stand-up%20comedy%20in%20addition%20to%20his%20content%20creation%2C%20and%20said%20he%20would%20never%20go%20back%20to%20a%20corporate%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20being%20my%20own%20boss.%20I%20love%20creating%20my%20own%20schedule%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20such%20a%20freeing%20feeling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-consultants-quit-mbb-big-four-content-creators-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774780081000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c71d0f8373a547629c7488%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-consultants-quit-mbb-big-four-content-creators-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gen%20Z%20consultants%20from%20firms%20like%20Bain%20and%20BCG%20are%20turning%20to%20social%20media%20and%20content%20creation%20as%20a%20new%2C%20lucrative%20exit%20opportunity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kvlamis%40businessinsider.com%20(Kelsey%20Vlamis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-consultants-quit-mbb-big-four-content-creators-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Developers%20warn%20flood%20of%20vibe-coded%20apps%20could%20slow%20Apple%20approvals%22%2C%22content%22%3