0taking%20longer%20than%20before.%20Some%20users%20on%20Reddit%20said%20they%20worry%20the%20review%20process%20could%20become%20stricter%20to%20prevent%20vibe-coded%20apps%20and%20AI%20slop%20from%20reaching%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20developers'%20frustrations%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20people%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-becoming-a-real-job-startups-entrepreneurship-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emaking%20careers%20out%20of%20vibe%20coding%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Platforms%20like%20Lovable%20have%20listed%20jobs%20calling%20for%20professional%20vibe%20coders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EForrester%20analyst%20Dipanjan%20Chatterjee%20said%20he%20expects%20Apple%20to%20err%20on%20the%20side%20of%20caution%20when%20approving%20apps%20for%20the%20App%20Store.%20A%20stricter%20process%20might%20frustrate%20developers%2C%20but%20it%20mitigates%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-slop-photos-videos-instagram-chatgpt-humans-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eamount%20of%20AI%20slop%20%3C%2Fa%3Eout%20there%2C%20he%20said.%20It'll%20have%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20more%20long-term%20solution%20soon%2C%20however.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20problem%20Apple%20can%20reject%20its%20way%20out%20of%3B%20as%20AI%20accelerates%20app%20creation%2C%20the%20company%20will%20have%20to%20evolve%20from%20artisanal%20gatekeeping%20to%20curation%20at%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20Chatterjee%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdevelopers-warn-flood-vibe-coded-apps-could-slow-apple-approvals-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774779301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6b4ae8e44c01630d3180a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdevelopers-warn-flood-vibe-coded-apps-could-