_blank%5C%22%3EMarch%2019%20speech%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20biggest%20names%20in%20private%20credit%20are%20facing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblackstone-private-credit-warning-signs-financial-crisis-risks-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erecord%20investor%20redemptions%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20criticism%20of%20their%20valuation%20policies%20and%20their%20exposure%20to%20troubled%20software%20companies.%20Private%20credit%20was%20only%20mentioned%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUyeda%20said%20that%20the%20government's%20role%20is%20not%20to%20protect%20Americans%20from%20potential%20investing%20mishaps%2C%20but%20to%20%26quot%3Bbuild%20and%20maintain%20the%20infrastructure%20that%20makes%20free%20markets%20possible.%26quot%3B%20To%20that%20end%2C%20he%20said%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20the%20government's%20role%20to%20impose%20its%20judgment%20as%20to%20what%20opportunities%20investors%20may%20pursue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20as%20more%20funds%20reported%20outflows%20or%20credit%20downgrades%2C%20a%20key%20Department%20of%20Labor%20rule%20that%20could%20shield%20retirement%20plans%20that%20offer%20private%20equity%20and%20credit%20from%20retiree%20lawsuits%20completed%20White%20House%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rules%20are%20a%20result%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-private-equity-retirement-plan-risk-401k-retail-investor-warning-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%20executive%20order%20%3C%2Fa%3Elast%20August%2C%20which%20instructed%20the%20DOL%20to%20help%20open%20401(k)s%20to%20private%20assets%2C%20with%20the%20SEC%20tasked%20as%20one%20agency%20that%20would%20consult%20with%20the%20DOL.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20the%20rule's%20text%20will%20become%20public%2C%20commencing%20a%2030-or%2060-day%20comment%20period%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20final%20review%20by%20the%20Office%20of%20Information%20and%20Regulatory%20Affairs.%20As%20bad%20news%20continues%20to%20mount%20for%20private%20credit%20firms%2C%20the%20push%20for%20your%20401(k)%20continues%20%E2%80%94%20raising%20the%20question%3A%20Is%20this%20the%20right%20moment%20to%20expand%20access%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Craig%20Copeland%2C%20the%20director%20of%20wealth%20benefits%20research%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretirement-savings-social-security-magic-number-how-much-money-need-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEmployee%20Benefit%20Research%20Institute%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3Bdiscussions%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20current%20market%20conditions%20are%20%26quot%3Bbeginning%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20%26quot%3Btremendous%20amount%20of%20momentum%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20money%20spent%20mean%20plans%20are%20continuing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20it's%20going%20to%20immediately%20slow%20down%20unless%20something%20really%20bad%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20Copeland%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c97901d-3683-4398-a4d1-202235ef3db6%5C%22%3EWhy%20are%20private%20markets%20going%20for%20401(k)s%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%2412%20trillion%20in%20defined-contribution%20cash%20represents%20a%20massive%20pool%20of%20money%20to%20help%20the%20private%20markets%20industry%20continue%20to%20grow%2C%20right%20as%20some%20institutional%20investors%20have%20decided%20to%20cut%20back%20on%20future%20private%20equity%20allocations.%20It's%20related%20to%20the%20industry%20push%20into%20the%20mass%20affluent%2C%20with%20funds%20offered%20to%20individual%2C%20wealthy%20investors%20through%20their%20financial%20advisors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20private%20markets%20industry%20has%20been%20eyeing%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-hot-investment-private-credit-retirement-savings-401k-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eentry%20into%20401(k)%20%3C%2Fa%3Eplans%20since%20at%20least%20the%20first%20Trump%20administration%2C%20as%20the%20threat%20of%20lawsuits%20from%20retirees%20kept%20retirement%20providers%20from%20jumping%20into%20private%20assets.%20'Litigation%20reform%2C'%20or%20protection%20from%20shareholder%20lawsuits%2C%20rose%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20wish%20list%20for%20the%20industry's%20biggest%20players%20since%20Trump's%20reelection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetirement%20funds%20are%20governed%20by%20the%20Employee%20Retirement%20Income%20Security%20Act%20of%201974%2C%20under%20which%20employers%20are%20fiduciaries%2C%20legally%20responsible%20for%20selecting%20investments%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20plan%20participants.%20This%20standard%20has%20historically%20pushed%20toward%20low-cost%2C%20liquid%20structures%20like%20mutual%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20wave%20of%20participant%20lawsuits%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-401k-fees-lawsuits-private-equity-apollo-kkr-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ealready%20slashed%20fees%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20traditional%20401(k)s%2C%20and%20those%20fees%20are%20substantially%20smaller%20than%20those%20charged%20by%20private%20credit%20and%20equity%20managers.%20Many%20in%20the%20industry%20believe%20these%20high%20fees%20are%20worthwhile%20and%20can%20lead%20to%20improved%20performance%2C%20though%20some%20are%20skeptical%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-returns-understanding-irr-mark-to-market-401k-investors-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eindustry's%20returns%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Uyeda%20called%20out%20this%20%26quot%3Bdisparity%26quot%3B%20between%20those%20who%20can%20invest%20in%20private%20assets%20and%20those%20who%20can't%20in%20his%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20teacher%20or%20firefighter%20whose%20retirement%20is%20managed%20by%20a%20public%20pension%20fund%20has%20benefited%20from%20meaningful%20private%20market%20exposure%20for%20years%2C%20if%20not%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20private%20sector%20worker%20saving%20through%20mutual%20funds%20in%20a%20401(k)%20plan%20has%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20pending%20DOL%20rule%20could%20create%20the%20exact%20conditions%20for%20a%20boom%20in%20private%20assets%20in%20401(k)%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20need%20to%20prudently%20include%20private%20assets%20in%20defined%20contribution%20plans%20because%20access%20alone%20is%20not%20enough%20if%20plan%20sponsors%20are%20deterred%20by%20litigation%20that%20second-guesses%20good-faith%20decisions%20with%20the%20benefit%20of%20hindsight%2C%26quot%3B%20Uyeda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22462f4d12-6a3d-459b-b500-9738c24f172a%5C%22%3EWhat%20about%20the%20liquidity%20criticisms%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EConcerns%20about%20the%20illiquidity%20of%20private%20assets%20are%20a%20%26quot%3Bfamiliar%26quot%3B%20part%20of%20the%20argument%20against%20adding%20them%20to%20retirement%20plans%2C%20said%20Uyeda.%20The%20very%20nature%20of%20private%20assets%20means%20they%20don't%20trade%20on%20public%20exchanges%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20can't%20be%20easily%20sold%20if%20a%20plan%20needs%20more%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUyeda%20said%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-market-analysis-outlook-equity-credit-ipo-acces-capitalism-openai-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bpremium%26quot%3B%20for%20illiquidity%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20actually%20be%20%26quot%3Bdesirable%26quot%3B%20for%20future%20retirees%2C%20who%20are%20long-term%20investors%20that%20don't%20typically%20need%20to%20access%20their%20savings%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20401(k)%20plans%20still%20require%20liquidity%20for%20workers%20who%20change%20jobs%20and%20retirement%20plans%2C%20for%20workers%20who%20do%20retire%2C%20and%20for%20people%20who%20withdraw%20from%20their%20funds%20in%20an%20emergency%2C%20with%20tax%20consequences.%20In%202025%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F401k-hardship-withdrawals-record-retirement-savings-investment-accounts-stock-market-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bhardship%20withdrawals%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Vanguard%20401(k)%20plans%20hit%20a%20record%2C%20with%206%25%20of%20participants%20pulling%20their%20money%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20industry's%20solution%20has%20been%20to%20package%20private%20assets%20alongside%20traditional%20public%2C%20liquid%20assets%20in%20structures%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Ftarget-date-funds%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etarget-date%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20to%20rely%20on%20repayments%20and%20continued%20worker%20contributions%20into%20their%20retirement%20plans%20to%20meet%20withdrawals.%20It%20has%20also%20highlighted%20private%20credit%20as%20a%20more%20liquid%20alternative%20to%20private%20equity%2C%20making%20it%20a%20mainstay%20of%20its%20retirement%20pitch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20narrative%20is%20currently%20being%20tested%2C%20with%20investors%20looking%20to%20withdraw%2011%25%20or%20more%20of%20their%20funds%20from%20certain%20non-traded%20retail%20private%20credit%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithin%20the%20last%20month%20and%20a%20half%2C%20we've%20seen%20exactly%20how%20liquid%20private%20credit%20is%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20Jim%20Baker%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20nonprofit%20watchdog%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmap-shows-private-equity-owned-hospitals-by-state-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPrivate%20Equity%20Stakeholder%20Project%2C%20said%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20describing%20the%20market%20as%20%26quot%3Bmelting%20down%26quot%3B%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22939d13cc-63b8-4c73-a4f8-2de3d110faea%5C%22%3EWhat%20does%20the%20turmoil%20mean%20for%20changes%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapollo-private-credit-firm-gate-redemptions-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERecord%20redemptions%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20private%20credit%20are%20matched%20by%20a%20challenging%20picture%20in%20private%20equity%2C%20with%20funds%20holding%20onto%20companies%20longer%20than%20typically%2C%20and%20payouts%20to%20investors%20are%20sluggish.%20Baker's%20organization%20sees%20the%20401(k)%20push%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbailout%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20struggling%20private%20capital%20industry%2C%20but%20unlike%20the%202008%20and%202009%20bailouts%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20with%20government%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20they're%20trying%20to%20bail%20out%20private%20equity%20and%20private%20credit%20with%20your%20and%20my%20retirement%20savings%2C%26quot%3B%20Baker%20said.%20He%20said%20that%20one%20would%20have%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bpsychopath%26quot%3B%20to%20stop%20retirees%20from%20suing%20their%20plan%20administrators%20in%20this%20current%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20say%20the%20comparison%20to%20retail%20funds%20misses%20the%20mark.%20Kevin%20Walsh%2C%20fiduciary%20practice%20leader%20at%20Groom%20Law%2C%20who%20works%20on%20both%20retail-oriented%20funds%20and%20retirement%20fund%20structures%2C%20said%20that%20in%20retail%20funds%2C%20where%20there%20are%20no%20penalties%20for%20withdrawing%20money%2C%20redemption%20limits%20exist%20to%20protect%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20these%20gates%20in%20place%20so%20that%20the%20investors%20who%20want%20to%20be%20there%20for%20the%20long%20run%20can't%20be%20forced%20to%20allow%20investors%20who%20want%20to%20get%20out%20quickly%20to%20mess%20with%20long-term%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20Walsh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20semi-liquid%20evergreen%20market%20today%2C%20where%20we're%20seeing%20the%20gating%2C%20that's%20a%20retail%20channel%2C%26quot%3B%20Walsh%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20401(k)%20space%20is%20an%20institutional%20channel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Epstein%2C%20the%20president%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20industry%20nonprofit%20Defined%20Contribution%20Alternatives%20Association%2C%20echoed%20that%20point%2C%20saying%20that%20no%20one%20is%20talking%20about%20adding%20the%20semi-liquid%20retail%20assets%20directly%20to%20a%20retirement%20plan%20lineup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFolks%20seem%20to%20be%20talking%20past%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20protection%20against%20lawsuits%20is%20in%20place%2C%20that%20doesn't%20guarantee%20adoption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlan%20sponsors%20are%20already%20dealing%20with%20complexities%20around%20other%20considerations%20like%20adding%20lifetime%20distribution%20options%2C%26quot%3B%20Michelle%20Capezza%2C%20an%20employee%20benefits%20lawyer%20at%20law%20firm%20Mintz%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20about%20rules%20that%20allow%20annuities%20in%20retirement%20plans.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20safe%20harbors%20for%20those%20options%2C%20yet%20they're%20still%20reluctant%20to%20do%20that%20type%20of%20diligence%20and%20add%20those%20types%20of%20features.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrivate%20credit's%20ability%20to%20weather%20this%20storm%2C%20which%20combines%20its%20own%20sectoral%20issues%20with%20a%20softening%20economy%20in%20the%20face%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-war-economic-impact-oil-prices-inflation-supply-el-erian-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20Iran%20War%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fiea-telling-people-work-from-home-as-oil-prices-soar-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epotential%20energy%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20could%20actually%20end%20up%20being%20a%20selling%20point%2C%20said%20Copeland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20may%20be%2C%20in%20some%20perverse%20way%2C%20a%20good%20thing%20to%20have%20this%20happen%20if%20it%20doesn't%20crater%2C%20if%20they%20can%20weather%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Copeland.%20%26quot%3BThen%2C%20they%20could%20say%20'We%20can%20handle%20a%20liquidity%20crisis%20in%20the%20direct%20investment%20market%2C%20and%20if%20we%20do%20it%20with%20additional%20liquidity%20on%20top%2C%20we%20should%20be%20all%20right.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-credit-troubles-retirement-funds-401k-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774778521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c7069e8e5f53c45ea2d10c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-credit-troubles-retirement-funds-401k-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Even%20as%20private%20credit%20faces%20redemptions%20and%20scrutiny%2C%20policymakers%20are%20moving%20closer%20to%20bringing%20it%20into%20Americans'%20retirement%20accounts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22anicoll%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Nicoll)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-credit-troubles-retirement-funds-401k-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hundreds%20of%20mourners%20gather%20in%20pouring%20rain%20for%20funerals%20of%20Lebanon%20journalists%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774778400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F26%2F03%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-mourners-funeral_7206145.jpg%3F20260329120329%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhundreds-of-mourners-gather-in-pouring-rain-for-funerals-of-lebanon-journalists-13525792%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hundreds%20of%20mourners%20turned%20out%20in%20the%20pouring%20rain%20in%20Beirut%20for%20the%20funerals%20of%20three%20journalists%20killed%20by%20Israeli%20strikes%20in%20southern%20Lebanon.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhundreds-of-mourners-gather-in-pouring-rain-f