was%20developing%20the%20capability%20to%20detect%20handwriting%20and%20convert%20it%20to%20text%2C%20and%20Dennis%20Ritchie%2C%20who%20created%20the%20C%20programming%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20dad's%20work%20with%20speech%20recognition%20and%20synthesis%20was%20the%20foundation%20for%20what%20I%20do%20today%20with%20generative%20AI.%20Everything%20I've%20built%20here%20has%20the%20same%20foundation%20he%20was%20working%20on%3A%20convolutional%20neural%20networks%2C%20which%20enable%20computers%20to%20process%20inputs%20like%20images%20and%20sound.%20It's%20really%20cool%20to%20see%20how%20that%20foundation%20has%20evolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22838%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Natalie%20and%20Mazin%20Gilbert%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bdb80c58b5806618e7cf71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22484%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENatalie%20Gilbert%20and%20her%20father%2C%20Mazin%20Gilbert.%3Cp%3EAT%26amp%3BT%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20early%20discoveries%20have%20enabled%20us%20to%20work%20with%20AI%20agents%20and%20make%20them%20more%20autonomous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20child%2C%20I%20was%20pretty%20much%20in%20my%20dad's%20office%20almost%20every%20day%20after%20school%2C%20and%20I%20remember%20watching%20him%20and%20his%20colleagues%20have%20heated%20discussions%20and%20draw%20crazy%20diagrams%20on%20the%20whiteboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20inspired%20me%20to%20start%20drawing%20my%20own%20decision%20trees%20and%20whatnot%20that%20were%20super%20nonsensical%2C%20but%20the%20experience%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20be%20creative%20and%20analytical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20side%20project%20my%20dad%20and%20I%20worked%20on%20together%20was%20called%20Dr%20Bot%2C%20which%20was%20an%20early%20iteration%20of%20a%20large%20language%20model%20that%20could%20assess%20your%20symptoms%20and%20tell%20you%20where%20to%20seek%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22da83ba17-0073-48ac-9d33-ef7aa4fc59a1%5C%22%3EFrom%20whiteboarding%20to%20coding%20and%20back%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20do%20with%20AI%20agents%20really%20boils%20down%20to%20a%20bunch%20of%20decision%20trees%20that%20reason%20through%20how%20to%20get%20from%20point%20A%20to%20point%20B.%20It%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewas%20something%20that%20I%20learned%20very%20early%20on%20with%20my%20dad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20human%20interaction%20that's%20increasingly%20important%20in%20the%20building%20of%20AI%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatt-salaries-revealed-how-much-pay-tech-workers-make-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAT%26amp%3BT's%20Chief%20Data%20Office%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we're%20working%20on%20a%20project%20that's%20transforming%20how%20people%20think%20about%20using%20HR%20technology%20within%20the%20company.%20We're%20basically%20eliminating%20the%20question%20of%20where%20to%20go%20to%20solve%20an%20HR%20problem%20by%20having%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatt-chatgpt-ai-openai-tech-workers-coding-generative-ai-translation-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20agent%20identify%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20relevant%20policy%20or%20procedure%20for%20a%20person's%20situation.%20That's%20no%20small%20matter%20in%20an%20organization%20as%20large%20and%20complicated%20as%20AT%26amp%3BT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Natalie%20Gilbert%20(L)%20with%20a%20colleague.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bdb8385b58f1f0f9335c7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENatalie%20Gilbert%20with%20a%20colleague%20at%20AT%26amp%3BT.%3Cp%3EAT%26amp%3BT%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20own%20work%2C%20I%20do%20use%20a%20coding%20copilot%2C%20or%20digital%20assistant%2C%20that%20helps%20me%20work%20a%20lot%20faster%2C%20but%20people%20who%20are%20developing%20AI%20tools%20still%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20technologies%20that%20underlie%20LLMs%20and%20machine%20learning%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2245baa22f-13f9-4c87-8dec-7d613f2d97a3%5C%22%3ENew%20AI%20tools%20are%20amazingly%20powerful%2C%20but%20they%20can't%20do%20everything%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaid-off-amazon-use-ai-protect-job-vibe-coding-lesson-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecopilots%20get%20more%20popular%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20people%20can%20run%20into%20trouble%20if%20they%20don't%20understand%20how%20those%20technologies%20fundamentally%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20know%20how%20the%20code%20is%20actually%20handling%20an%20edge-case%20scenario%2C%20then%20your%20AI%20tools%20aren't%20going%20to%20be%20any%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20people%20need%20to%20learn%20something%20new%20every%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20see%20changing%20with%20large%20language%20models%20is%20that%20they%20are%20much%20more%20natural-language-focused%20rather%20than%20coded.%20That%20means%20I%20actually%20spend%20most%20of%20my%20time%20doing%20prompt%20engineering%2C%20which%20isn't%20coding%20at%20all%3B%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatt-open-source-ai-better-than-chatgpt-customer-service-calls-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eusing%20natural%20language%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20machines%20to%20understand%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20sort%20of%20ironic%2C%20because%20this%20is%20another%20form%20of%20what%20my%20dad%20did%2030%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20has%20changed%20so%20drastically%20in%20my%20lifetime%2C%20and%20now%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20representing%20him%20and%20representing%20his%20legacy.%20Continuing%20the%20work%20that%20he%20did%20feels%20surreal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22h